Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.30,0:26:27.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要阻止他们  灭灭他们的风头\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We gotta stop 'em and rob 'em of their advantages
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.34,0:26:29.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上帝赐我们毅力  我们要坚定立场\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Let's take a stand with the stamina God has granted us
