Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.98,0:26:51.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,英军攻城略地  我军人心惶惶\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They're skittish as the British cut the city up
