Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.55,0:27:03.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们夜奔行军  远远望着曼哈顿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We ride at midnight, Manhattan in the distance
