Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.04,0:27:13.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚隆·伯尔  长官  可以说说我的想法吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Aaron Burr, sir. Permission to state my case?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.88,0:27:14.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你请便\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}As you were.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.85,0:27:18.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长官  我曾是蒙哥马利将军麾下的上尉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sir, I was a captain under General Montgomery
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.22,0:27:20.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他在魁北克颈部中弹\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Until he caught a bullet in the neck in Quebec
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.84,0:27:24.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总而言之  我觉得自己能帮上忙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, in summary, I think that I could be of some assistance
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.48,0:27:28.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我敬佩您一直从远处向英军开火\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I admire how you keep firing on the British from a distance
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.30,0:27:30.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有几个问题  想提几个建议\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I have some questions, a couple of suggestions
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.86,0:27:33.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要抗击  而不是西逃\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}on how to fight instead of fleeing west
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.02,0:27:33.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-请讲  -那么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Yes? - Well--
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.89,0:27:36.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长官  您要见我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Your Excellency, you wanted to see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.24,0:27:38.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汉密尔顿  进来  你认识伯尔吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hamilton, come in. Have you met Burr?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.11,0:27:39.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-认识  长官  我们总碰到  -我们总碰到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Yes, sir. We keep meeting. - We keep meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.76,0:27:41.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我刚才说  长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}As I was saying, sir,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.04,0:27:43.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我期待您的战略发挥成效\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I look forward to seeing your strategy play out.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.58,0:27:44.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-伯尔  -长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Burr? - Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.36,0:27:46.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出去后把门关上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Close the door on your way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.85,0:27:49.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做错什么了吗  长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Have I done something wrong, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.60,0:27:50.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正相反\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}On the contrary
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.88,0:27:53.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫你过来是因为我们的胜算太渺茫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I called you here because our odds are beyond scary
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.87,0:27:55.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的大名如雷贯耳\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Your reputation precedes you
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.68,0:27:56.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-但我忍不住发笑  -长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- But I have to laugh. - Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.97,0:27:59.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汉密尔顿  怎么就没人把你招致麾下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hamilton, how come no one can get you on their staff?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.66,0:27:59.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sir--
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.94,0:28:02.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别误会我  你是个有名望的年轻人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Don't get me wrong. You're a young man of great renown
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.96,0:28:05.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在市区战斗时你偷了英军的火炮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I know you stole British cannons when we were still downtown
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.90,0:28:08.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纳瑟内尔·格林和亨利·诺克斯都想将你收入靡下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Nathanael Greene and Henry Knox wanted to hire you
