Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.68,0:36:08.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回忆起那晚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I remember that night
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.63,0:36:11.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可能会为此后悔一辈子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I just might regret that night for the rest of my days
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.58,0:36:12.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还记得那群年轻气盛的军人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I remember those soldier boys
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.88,0:36:15.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,急不可耐地想要讨我们欢心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}tripping over themselves to win our praise
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.43,0:36:17.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还记得那如梦似幻的烛光\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I remember that dreamlike candlelight
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.23,0:36:19.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如此虚无缥缈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Like a dream that you can't quite place
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.30,0:36:20.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是亚历山大\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But, Alexander
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.56,0:36:24.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我永远忘不了与你初见的那一天\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll never forget the first time I saw your face
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.34,0:36:26.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就此不同\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I have never been the same
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.56,0:36:30.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那睿智的双眼  精瘦的体格\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Intelligent eyes in a hunger-pang frame
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.42,0:36:33.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你向我问声好  我便忘却自己姓名\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And when you said "Hi," I forgot my dang name
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.98,0:36:36.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挑拨起我心中的火焰  燃遍全身\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Set my heart aflame, every part aflame
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.97,0:36:38.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是场游戏\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is not a game
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.73,0:36:42.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我看来  你好像从未满足过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You strike me as a woman who has never been satisfied
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.57,0:36:46.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不懂你在说什么  你逾越了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm sure I don't know what you mean, you forget yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.34,0:36:50.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和我一样  我就从不满足\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're like me, I'm never satisfied
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.57,0:36:52.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.49,0:36:55.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从未满足\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I have never been satisfied
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.85,0:36:58.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫安洁莉卡·斯凯勒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My name is Angelica Schuyler
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.06,0:37:00.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚历山大·汉密尔顿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Alexander Hamilton
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.44,0:37:02.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你家世如何\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Where's your family from?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.55,0:37:06.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不重要  志向千千万  我才刚开始\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Unimportant, there's a million things I haven't done
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.21,0:37:09.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过你等着瞧  你等着瞧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But just you wait, just you wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.11,0:37:11.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道这就是斗智斗勇\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So, so, so, so this is what it feels like to match wits
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.72,0:37:13.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,棋逢对手的感觉  这里头肯定有诈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}With someone at your level, what the hell is the catch?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.46,0:37:15.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这感觉如同重见光明\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's the feeling of freedom of seeing the light
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.32,0:37:17.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如同富兰克林风筝迎闪电\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's Ben Franklin with a key and a kite
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.01,0:37:17.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看见了吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You see it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.80,0:37:19.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三两分钟的交谈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The conversation lasted two minutes, maybe three minutes
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.84,0:37:21.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们便情投意合\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Everything we said in total agreement
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.54,0:37:23.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像是一场梦  一支舞\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's a dream and it's a bit of a dance
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.31,0:37:25.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,故作姿态  摆明立场\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A bit of a posture, it's a bit of a stance
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.31,0:37:27.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他虽风流  但我也愿意给个机会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He's a bit of a flirt, but I'mma give it a chance
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.17,0:37:29.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,询问起家况  他竟那样答复\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I asked about his family, did you see his answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.20,0:37:31.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他局促不安  眼神躲闪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}His hands started fidgeting, he looked askance
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.08,0:37:33.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他身无分文  摸爬滚打\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He's penniless, he's flying by the seat of his pants
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.17,0:37:35.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是那样一表人才\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Handsome, boy, does he know it
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.08,0:37:37.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,零星的胡须  稚气仍未脱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Peach fuzz, and he can't even grow it
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.24,0:37:38.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想带他远远逃离这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I wanna take him far away from this place
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.74,0:37:40.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但转身看见我的妹妹  她已经\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Then I turn and see my sister's face and she is...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.00,0:37:42.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情难自禁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Helpless
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.20,0:37:44.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道她已经\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And I know she is...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.81,0:37:45.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情难自禁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Helpless
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.93,0:37:48.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的眼神已经\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And her eyes are just...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.60,0:37:50.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情难自禁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Helpless
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.09,0:37:56.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与此同时我意识到三大基本真理\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And I realize three fundamental truths at the exact same time
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.69,0:37:59.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你要带我去哪里  -我要改变你的人生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Where are you taking me? - I'm about to change your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.75,0:38:01.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那恭敬不如从命\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Then by all means, lead the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.38,0:38:02.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Number one
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.88,0:38:06.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只用嫁给一个富人家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm a girl in a world in which my only job is to marry rich
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.46,0:38:10.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs14\b0\bord0\shad0}事实上她父亲有数个儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.46,0:38:07.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是家父不曾育有儿子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My father has no sons,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.64,0:38:10.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以得靠我来攀附权贵\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}so I'm the one who has to social climb for one
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.04,0:38:11.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我是最聪明的长女\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}'Cause I'm the oldest and the wittiest
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.55,0:38:14.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而纽约城满是流言蜚语\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And the gossip in New York City is insidious
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.32,0:38:15.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然亚历山大身无分文\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And Alexander is penniless
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.93,0:38:18.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的爱意也丝毫不会减\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ha, that doesn't mean I want him any less
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.50,0:38:20.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊丽莎白·斯凯勒  幸会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Elizabeth Schuyler. It's a pleasure to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.97,0:38:23.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-斯凯勒  -我妹妹\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Schuyler? - My sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.02,0:38:24.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Number two
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.53,0:38:26.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他追求我  只因我是斯凯勒家千金\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He's after me, 'Cause I'm a Schuyler sister
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.58,0:38:28.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这能提升他的地位\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That elevates his status
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.16,0:38:32.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抛开这点也太天真  正是因此\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'd have to be naive to set that aside, maybe that is why
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.19,0:38:36.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才给他介绍伊莱莎  如今已是他的新娘\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I introduced him to Eliza, now that's his bride
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.08,0:38:38.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干得好  安洁莉卡  他说得对\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Nice going, Angelica, he was right
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.09,0:38:40.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你永远不会满足\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You will never be satisfied
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.30,0:38:41.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢你浴血奋战\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Thank you for all your service.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.69,0:38:43.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倘若我们相识的代价就是开战\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If it takes fighting a war for us to meet,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.18,0:38:44.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那这仗打得也值了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}it will have been worth it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.64,0:38:46.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不打扰你们了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll leave you to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.72,0:38:48.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第三\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Number three
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.20,0:38:51.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对我妹妹了如指掌\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I know my sister Like I know my own mind
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.41,0:38:55.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再也不会有人像她那般纯真善良\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You will never find anyone as trusting or as kind
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.52,0:38:59.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若我对她诉衷肠  她会默默成全\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If I tell her that I love him, she'd be silently resigned
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.16,0:39:01.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他将属于我  而她会故作轻松\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He'd be mine, she would say, "I'm fine"
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.99,0:39:03.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但那都是假装\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}She'd be lying
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.78,0:39:08.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每个夜晚  我都会想起亚历山大的双眸\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But when I fantasize at night, it's Alexander's eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.11,0:39:11.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会幻想  若我没有断然评判他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}As I romanticize what might have been
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.48,0:39:15.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在又会如何\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If I hadn't sized him up so quickly
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.21,0:39:21.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少亲爱的伊莱莎是他的妻子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}At least my dear Eliza's his wife
