Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.76,1:00:12.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暗号是  "罗尚博"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The code word is, "Rochambeau"
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.76,1:00:13.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs14\b0\bord0\shad0}音似"向前冲"
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.43,1:00:13.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-明白吗  -罗尚博\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Dig me? - Rochambeau
Dialogue: 0,1:00:13.60,1:00:15.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,命令已经下达  伙计们向前冲\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You have your orders now, go, men, go
Dialogue: 0,1:00:15.60,1:00:18.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就此揭开  独立大业\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And so the American experiment begins
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.02,1:00:19.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至交兄弟  征战八方\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}With my friends all scattered to the winds
Dialogue: 0,1:00:19.98,1:00:23.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,南卡罗莱纳  劳伦斯写出英勇的新篇章\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Laurens is in South Carolina, redefining bravery
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.06,1:00:25.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有奴隶不再  自由才会到来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We'll never be free Until we end slavery
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.86,1:00:27.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当英军鱼溃鸟散\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}When we finally drive the British away
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.78,1:00:29.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉法耶特早已经\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Lafayette is there waiting
Dialogue: 0,1:00:29.15,1:00:30.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,守在切萨皮克湾\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}In Chesapeake Bay
Dialogue: 0,1:00:30.70,1:00:32.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们何以确信  此计必将凯旋\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How did we know that this plan would work?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:32.53,1:00:34.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我方内应  深入敌军  是的没错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We had a spy on the inside, that's right
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.91,1:00:36.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赫丘利·穆里根\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hercules Mulligan!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.12,1:00:37.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裁缝监视英国政府\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A tailor spying on the British government
Dialogue: 0,1:00:37.75,1:00:39.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我量体裁衣  我搜集信息\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I take their measurements, information
Dialogue: 0,1:00:39.29,1:00:40.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我瞒天过海\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And then I smuggle it up
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.62,1:00:42.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为革命盟友通风报信\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}To my brother's revolutionary covenant
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.58,1:00:45.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,携手"自由之子"  有种就来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm running with the Sons of Liberty and I am loving it!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.58,1:00:47.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs14\b0\bord0\shad0}反抗英国统治的激进秘密组织\N曾发动波士顿茶党事件  故俗称波士顿茶党
Dialogue: 0,1:00:45.42,1:00:47.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,招惹无赖  就是自讨苦吃\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}See, that's what happens when you up against the ruffians
Dialogue: 0,1:00:47.88,1:00:50.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身陷困境  谁来收烂摊子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We in the shit now, somebody's gotta shovel it
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.22,1:00:52.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赫丘利·穆里根  早已声名远扬\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hercules Mulligan, I need no introduction
Dialogue: 0,1:00:52.34,1:00:55.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一次次被击倒  又一次次矗立\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}When you knock me down I get the fuck back up again!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:02.35,1:01:03.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向左  向右  稳住\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Left! Right! Hold!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.52,1:01:06.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前进\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Go!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.11,1:01:10.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无所畏惧  所向披靡\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What? What? What?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:24.67,1:01:25.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七日征战\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}After a week of fighting
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.96,1:01:28.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红衣军官  走上城墙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A young man in a red coat stands on a parapet
Dialogue: 0,1:01:29.92,1:01:33.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挥起白绢  我们放下枪炮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We lower our guns as he frantically waves a white handkerchief
Dialogue: 0,1:01:34.93,1:01:36.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战争就这样终结\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And just like that, it's over.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:36.18,1:01:38.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们照顾伤员  我们缅怀死者\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We tend to our wounded, we count our dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.89,1:01:40.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑人士兵  白人士兵  一同思忖\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Black and white soldiers wonder alike
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.89,1:01:42.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自由是否触手可及\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}if this really means freedom.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:42.73,1:01:44.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为时尚早\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:44.81,1:01:46.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们谈判投降条件\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We negotiate the terms of surrender.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:47.27,1:01:49.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看见乔治·华盛顿笑容满面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I see George Washington smile.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:49.73,1:01:51.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们押解英军出城\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We escort their men out of Yorktown.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.20,1:01:54.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人所剩无几  溃不成军\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They stagger home single file.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:54.20,1:01:56.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,民众走上街头  万人空巷\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Tens of thousands of people flood the streets.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:57.16,1:01:59.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人们欢呼雀跃  教堂钟声齐天\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There are screams and church bells ringing,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:59.54,1:02:01.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人落荒而逃\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and as our fallen foes retreat,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:01.29,1:02:03.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人们把酒言欢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I hear the drinking song they're singing.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:04.25,1:02:08.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界天翻地覆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The world turned upside down
Dialogue: 0,1:02:08.88,1:02:13.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界天翻地覆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The world turned upside down
Dialogue: 0,1:02:13.80,1:02:18.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界天翻地覆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The world turned upside down
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.72,1:02:22.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界天翻地覆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The world turned upside down
Dialogue: 0,1:02:22.39,1:02:26.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn微软雅黑\fs15\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}天翻地覆  天翻地覆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Down, down, down, down
Dialogue: 0,1:02:26.40,1:02:28.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为美利坚自由而战  为法兰西自由而战\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Freedom for America! Freedom for France!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.61,1:02:32.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn微软雅黑\fs15\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}天翻地覆  天翻地覆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Down, down, down
Dialogue: 0,1:02:30.94,1:02:33.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,建立新的国家  迎接我的儿子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Gotta start a new nation, gotta meet my son
Dialogue: 0,1:02:33.45,1:02:36.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn微软雅黑\fs15\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}天翻地覆  天翻地覆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Down, down, down
Dialogue: 0,1:02:35.78,1:02:36.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们胜利了  我们胜利了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We won! We won!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:36.95,1:02:38.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们胜利了  我们胜利了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We won! We won!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:38.41,1:02:45.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界天翻地覆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The world turned upside down
Dialogue: 0,1:03:14.36,1:03:16.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They say
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.67,1:03:22.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愿替我承担  战争代价\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The price of my war's not a price that they're willing to pay
Dialogue: 0,1:03:22.70,1:03:25.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愚蠢至极\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Insane
Dialogue: 0,1:03:25.22,1:03:26.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你勾结法国人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You cheat with the French
Dialogue: 0,1:03:26.97,1:03:30.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法国和西班牙  同时对我开战\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now I'm fighting with France and with Spain
Dialogue: 0,1:03:30.63,1:03:32.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好忧伤\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm so blue
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.70,1:03:38.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以为你走时  我们约法三章\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I thought that we made an arrangement when you went away
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.51,1:03:42.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要唯我是瞻\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You were mine to subdue
Dialogue: 0,1:03:42.03,1:03:45.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算现在  我们渐行渐远\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, even despite our estrangement
Dialogue: 0,1:03:45.53,1:03:51.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我依旧要问你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've got a small query for you
Dialogue: 0,1:03:53.06,1:03:57.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一步何处去  你已获得自由\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What comes next? You've been freed
Dialogue: 0,1:03:57.38,1:04:01.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可你是否留意  掌权何其不易\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Do you know how hard it is to lead?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:01.07,1:04:03.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如今你要自立\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're on your own
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.00,1:04:05.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真棒棒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Awesome, wow
Dialogue: 0,1:04:05.28,1:04:09.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可你是否明晰  今后何去何从\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Do you have a clue what happens now?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:09.15,1:04:13.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沧海桑田  王朝兴替\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oceans rise, empires fall
Dialogue: 0,1:04:13.46,1:04:17.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手握大权  进退两难\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's much harder when it's all your call
Dialogue: 0,1:04:17.41,1:04:22.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大洋彼岸  孤掌难鸣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All alone across the sea
Dialogue: 0,1:04:22.20,1:04:26.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待到民怨沸腾日\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}When your people say they hate you
Dialogue: 0,1:04:26.22,1:04:30.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可别向我来乞求\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Don't come crawling back to me
Dialogue: 0,1:04:44.33,1:04:50.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如今你要自立\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're on your own
Dialogue: 0,1:05:10.61,1:05:15.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宝贝西奥多莎  我该如何表达\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Dear Theodosia, what to say to you
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.14,1:05:18.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的双眸如我  名字随你妈妈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You have my eyes you have your mother's name
Dialogue: 0,1:05:18.57,1:05:22.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当你呱呱坠地\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}When you came into the world, you cried
Dialogue: 0,1:05:22.37,1:05:25.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已满怀情愫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And it broke my heart
Dialogue: 0,1:05:27.67,1:05:32.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时刻为你守护\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm dedicating every day to you
Dialogue: 0,1:05:32.36,1:05:35.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从不曾想过  眷恋家庭生活\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Domestic life was never quite my style
Dialogue: 0,1:05:35.96,1:05:38.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当你笑容洋溢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}When you smile
Dialogue: 0,1:05:38.82,1:05:41.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已无力抗拒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You knock me out, I fall apart
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.48,1:05:44.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾自诩伶俐\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And I thought I was so smart
Dialogue: 0,1:05:44.23,1:05:48.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和这个国家  一同慢慢长大\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You will come of age with our young nation
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.25,1:05:50.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要为你浴血奋战\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We'll bleed and fight for you
Dialogue: 0,1:05:50.40,1:05:52.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要为你披襟斩棘\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We'll make it right for you
Dialogue: 0,1:05:52.83,1:05:56.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若是我们能夯实根基\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If we lay a strong enough foundation
Dialogue: 0,1:05:56.77,1:05:58.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们将把它传承于你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We'll pass it on to you
Dialogue: 0,1:05:58.92,1:06:02.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们给你整个天地  有朝一日\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We'll give the world to you and you'll blow us all away
