Dialogue: 0,1:09:09.79,1:09:12.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽管我们同时起家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Even though we started at the very same time
Dialogue: 0,1:09:12.38,1:09:14.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚历山大迅速崭露头角\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Alexander Hamilton began to climb
