Dialogue: 0,1:09:23.73,1:09:25.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们是否知道  我们正在创造历史\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Are you aware that we're making history?
