Dialogue: 0,1:09:34.04,1:09:35.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是合作律师  汉密尔顿  你坐下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Co-counsel. Hamilton, sit down
Dialogue: 0,1:09:35.46,1:09:37.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的当事人李维·维克斯是无辜的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Our client, Levi Weeks, is innocent
