Dialogue: 0,1:09:49.02,1:09:51.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种态度  早晚万劫不复\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Soon that attitude may be your doom
Dialogue: 0,1:09:51.64,1:09:54.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为何笔耕不辍  仿佛时日无多\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Why do you write like you're running out of time?
