Dialogue: 0,1:10:02.40,1:10:05.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,腐败堕落  我们早已司空见惯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Corruption's such an old song that we can sing along in harmony
