Dialogue: 0,1:10:22.98,1:10:25.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汉密尔顿  出席制宪会议\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hamilton, at the Constitutional Convention
Dialogue: 0,1:10:25.67,1:10:28.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我被选中  参加制宪会议\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I was chosen for the Constitutional Convention
Dialogue: 0,1:10:28.27,1:10:30.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为纽约青年代表\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There as a New York junior delegate
Dialogue: 0,1:10:30.75,1:10:33.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要说的话有些刺耳\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now, what I'm going to say may sound indelicate...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:33.47,1:10:36.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在会上提出自己对政体的提议\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Goes and proposes his own form of government
Dialogue: 0,1:10:36.03,1:10:37.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn微软雅黑\fs15\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:36.24,1:10:38.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对新政体他有自己的计划\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}His own plan for a new form of government
Dialogue: 0,1:10:38.34,1:10:39.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn微软雅黑\fs15\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:38.63,1:10:41.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,六小时唇枪舌战  议员们神思倦怠\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Talks for six hours, the convention is listless
Dialogue: 0,1:10:41.32,1:10:42.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小伙有头脑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Bright young man
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.17,1:10:43.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这人谁啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yo, who the eff is this?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:43.90,1:10:46.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为何你总直抒己见\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Why do you always say what you believe?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:46.52,1:10:49.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为何你总直抒己见\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Why do you always say what you believe?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:49.12,1:10:54.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每句宣言都令你成为众矢之的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Every proclamation guarantees free ammunition for your enemies
Dialogue: 0,1:10:54.34,1:10:56.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为何笔耕不辍  仿佛不合时宜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Why do you write like it's going out of style?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:56.92,1:10:59.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日夜笔耕不辍  仿佛不合时宜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Write day and night like it's going out of style
Dialogue: 0,1:10:59.48,1:11:02.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天口诛笔伐  仿佛不合时宜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Every day you fight like it's going out of style
Dialogue: 0,1:11:02.09,1:11:03.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你少掺和\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Do what you do
Dialogue: 0,1:11:05.16,1:11:05.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚历山大\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Alexander
Dialogue: 0,1:11:05.80,1:11:07.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚隆·伯尔  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Aaron Burr, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:07.08,1:11:08.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已是午夜了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, it's the middle of the night.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:08.32,1:11:09.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们能谈谈吗  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Can we confer, sir?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:09.76,1:11:12.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-是法务问题吗  -是的  这对我来说很重要\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Is this a legal matter? - Yes, and it's important to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:12.35,1:11:15.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你有什么需要  -伯尔  你做律师比我在行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- What do you need? - Burr, you're a better lawyer than me.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:15.25,1:11:15.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:15.75,1:11:17.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道我说话又多又糙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I know I talk too much, I'm abrasive
Dialogue: 0,1:11:17.65,1:11:20.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在法庭上十分出色  语言干练而有说服力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're incredible in court. You're succinct, persuasive
Dialogue: 0,1:11:20.54,1:11:22.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的当事人需要有力的辩护  你能搞定\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My client needs a strong defense. You're the solution
Dialogue: 0,1:11:22.94,1:11:26.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你的当事人是谁  -新美国《宪法》\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Uh, who's your client? - The new US Constitution.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:26.13,1:11:27.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-不行  -听我说完\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- No. - Hear me out.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:27.31,1:11:28.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没门\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No way.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:28.03,1:11:30.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一系列匿名发表的文章\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A series of essays anonymously published
Dialogue: 0,1:11:30.67,1:11:32.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向公众声援宪法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}defending the document to the public
Dialogue: 0,1:11:32.80,1:11:34.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-没人会读的  -我认为有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- No one'll read it. - I disagree.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:34.35,1:11:35.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果失败了呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And if it fails?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:35.19,1:11:36.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伯尔  因此才需要它\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Burr, that's why we need it.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:36.37,1:11:39.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-《宪法》一塌糊涂  -因此才需要修订\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- The Constitution's a mess. - So it needs amendments.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:39.10,1:11:41.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-充满矛盾  -独立也是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- It's full of contradictions. - So is independence.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:41.48,1:11:44.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-万事开头难  -不  不行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- We have to start somewhere. - No. No way.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:44.35,1:11:46.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你在犯错误  -晚安\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- You're making a mistake. - Good night.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:47.13,1:11:49.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在等什么  你还犹豫什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What are you waiting for? What do you stall for?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:49.68,1:11:52.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-什么  -我们打赢了战争  图什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- What? - We won the war. What was it all for?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:52.51,1:11:54.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你支持新《宪法》吗  -当然\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Do you support this Constitution? - Of course.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:54.62,1:11:57.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-那就为它辩护  -万一你下错注呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Then defend it. - What if you're backing the wrong horse?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.53,1:12:00.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伯尔  我们一起学习  奋战  杀敌\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Burr, we studied and we fought and we killed
Dialogue: 0,1:12:00.01,1:12:02.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只为如今我们所建国家的信念\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}for the notion of a nation we now get to build
Dialogue: 0,1:12:02.66,1:12:05.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪怕此生仅有一次  你也应骄傲地表态\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}For once in your life, take a stand with pride
Dialogue: 0,1:12:05.33,1:12:07.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不明白你怎能袖手旁观\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't understand how you stand to the side
Dialogue: 0,1:12:07.32,1:12:11.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要将所有计划深藏不露\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I will keep all my plans close to my chest
Dialogue: 0,1:12:11.58,1:12:12.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等待  等待  等待\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Wait for it, wait for it, wait...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:12.58,1:12:17.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要作壁上观  见机行事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll wait here and see which way the wind will blow
Dialogue: 0,1:12:17.66,1:12:20.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要静观其变\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm taking my time
Dialogue: 0,1:12:20.26,1:12:22.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看着国家诞生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}watching the afterbirth of a nation
Dialogue: 0,1:12:22.78,1:12:25.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看着矛盾激化\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}watching the tension grow
Dialogue: 0,1:12:29.18,1:12:30.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我将向伦敦起航\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I am sailing off to London
Dialogue: 0,1:12:30.99,1:12:34.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与一个慷慨多金的人同往\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm accompanied by someone who always pays
Dialogue: 0,1:12:34.69,1:12:36.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我找到一位富有的丈夫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I have found a wealthy husband
Dialogue: 0,1:12:34.69,1:12:40.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs14\b0\bord0\shad0}事实上安洁莉卡与汉密尔顿相遇时已嫁为人妇\N她与丈夫育有三女五子
Dialogue: 0,1:12:36.48,1:12:40.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他将令我余生衣食无忧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}who will keep me in comfort for all my days
Dialogue: 0,1:12:40.28,1:12:41.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不算有趣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He is not a lot of fun
Dialogue: 0,1:12:41.85,1:12:45.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但论口才  谁也不可与你同日而语\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but there's no one who can match you for turn of phrase
Dialogue: 0,1:12:45.88,1:12:49.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我的亚历山大  -安洁莉卡\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- My Alexander - Angelica
Dialogue: 0,1:12:49.37,1:12:52.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别忘记写信\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Don't forget to write
Dialogue: 0,1:12:52.52,1:12:54.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看你如今的成就\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Look at where you are
Dialogue: 0,1:12:55.01,1:12:57.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想想你曾一无所有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Look at where you started
Dialogue: 0,1:12:57.16,1:12:59.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还活着就是个奇迹\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The fact that you're alive is a miracle
Dialogue: 0,1:12:59.80,1:13:02.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要你活着便已足够\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Just stay alive, that would be enough
Dialogue: 0,1:13:03.11,1:13:07.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若你能分给妻子一点时间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And if your wife could share a fraction of your time
Dialogue: 0,1:13:07.96,1:13:11.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若我能为你带来安宁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If I could grant you peace of mind
Dialogue: 0,1:13:11.44,1:13:13.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那便足够吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Would that be enough?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:13.37,1:13:16.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚历山大与詹姆斯·麦迪逊和约翰·杰伊联手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Alexander joins forces with James Madison and John Jay
Dialogue: 0,1:13:16.47,1:13:17.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,写下一系列文章\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to write a series of essays
Dialogue: 0,1:13:17.82,1:13:20.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为新美国《宪法》辩护\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}defending the new United States Constitution
Dialogue: 0,1:13:20.19,1:13:22.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,题为《联邦论》\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}entitled "The Federalist Papers"
Dialogue: 0,1:13:23.04,1:13:25.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,计划是共写25篇文章\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The plan was to write a total of 25 essays,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:25.49,1:13:27.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由三人平分工作量\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the work divided evenly among the three men.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:29.61,1:13:33.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最终  他们在六个月间写出85篇文章\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}In the end, they wrote 85 essays in the span of six months.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:34.01,1:13:36.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,约翰·杰伊写了五篇后病倒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}John Jay got sick after writing five.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:37.12,1:13:39.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,詹姆斯·麦迪逊写了29篇\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}James Madison wrote 29.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:39.85,1:13:43.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其余51篇由汉密尔顿所写\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hamilton wrote the other 51!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:43.94,1:13:46.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为何笔耕不辍  仿佛时日无多\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How do you write like you're running out of time?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:46.49,1:13:49.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日夜笔耕不辍  仿佛时日无多\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Write day and night like you're running out of time
Dialogue: 0,1:13:49.06,1:13:51.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天口诛笔伐  仿佛时日无多\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Every day you fight like you're running out of time
Dialogue: 0,1:13:51.68,1:13:54.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时日无多  是否时日无多\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Running out of time? Are you running out of time?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:54.26,1:13:57.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为何笔耕不辍  仿佛没有明天\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How do you write like tomorrow won't arrive?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:57.06,1:13:59.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为何笔耕不辍  仿佛命系笔尖\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How do you write like you need it to survive?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:59.85,1:14:02.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为何笔耕不辍  时刻争分夺秒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How do you write every second you're alive?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:02.37,1:14:05.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,争分夺秒  争分夺秒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Every second you're alive, every second you're alive
Dialogue: 0,1:14:06.34,1:14:08.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们要我领导\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They're asking me to lead
