Dialogue: 0,1:19:20.91,1:19:23.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托马斯  我们正处于一场斗争\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Thomas, we are engaged in a battle
Dialogue: 0,1:19:23.49,1:19:26.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事关国家精神\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}for our nation's very soul
Dialogue: 0,1:19:26.34,1:19:29.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能帮我们摆脱泥潭吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Can you get us out of the mess we're in?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:30.42,1:19:33.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汉密尔顿的新财政方案\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hamilton's new financial plan is nothing less
Dialogue: 0,1:19:30.42,1:19:36.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs14\b0\bord0\shad0}汉密尔顿意图建立美国中央银行\N旨在让联邦政府掌控财政
Dialogue: 0,1:19:33.84,1:19:36.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全然就是政府管制\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}than government control
Dialogue: 0,1:19:36.40,1:19:39.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直单枪匹马为南方抗争\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've been fighting for the South alone
Dialogue: 0,1:19:39.80,1:19:41.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去哪了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Where have you been?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:41.60,1:19:43.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法国  怎么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}France. What?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:43.61,1:19:45.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们必须赢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We have to win.
