Dialogue: 0,1:19:47.83,1:19:48.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我错过了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What did I miss?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:48.86,1:19:51.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn微软雅黑\fs15\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}我回家来就为这个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've come home to this?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:50.93,1:19:54.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一头扎入政治深渊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Headfirst into a political abyss
Dialogue: 0,1:19:54.22,1:19:56.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一头扎入深渊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Headfirst into the abyss
Dialogue: 0,1:19:56.31,1:19:58.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天首次参加内阁会议\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I have my first cabinet meeting today
Dialogue: 0,1:19:58.91,1:20:01.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得想想该说什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I guess I better think of something to say
Dialogue: 0,1:20:01.59,1:20:05.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已启程  定要弄个水落石出\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm already on my way. Let's get to the bottom of this
Dialogue: 0,1:20:05.28,1:20:07.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我错过了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What did I miss?
