Dialogue: 0,1:20:11.48,1:20:14.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰斐逊先生  我是亚历山大·汉密尔顿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Jefferson? Alexander Hamilton
Dialogue: 0,1:20:14.27,1:20:19.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰斐逊先生  欢迎回家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Jefferson, welcome home
Dialogue: 0,1:20:19.78,1:20:22.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰斐逊先生  欢迎回家  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Jefferson, welcome home, sir
Dialogue: 0,1:20:22.79,1:20:25.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在巴黎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You've been off in Paris
Dialogue: 0,1:20:25.94,1:20:30.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待了好久\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}For so long!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:30.51,1:20:32.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我错过了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So what did I miss?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:39.64,1:20:41.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女士们先生们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ladies and gentlemen,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:41.65,1:20:44.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们从世界各地远道而来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}you could've been anywhere in the world tonight,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:44.56,1:20:47.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与我们相聚纽约市\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but you're here with us in New York City.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:47.42,1:20:51.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备好参加内阁会议了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Are you ready for a cabinet meeting?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:52.49,1:20:54.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本次的议题是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The issue on the table:
Dialogue: 0,1:20:54.23,1:20:55.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汉密尔顿部长的提案\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Secretary Hamilton's plan to
Dialogue: 0,1:20:55.99,1:20:58.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,承担州债  建立国家银行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}assume state debt and establish a national bank.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:58.86,1:21:01.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰斐逊国务卿  请您发言\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Secretary Jefferson, you have the floor, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:02.40,1:21:04.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"生命权  自由权和追求幸福的权利"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"Life, liberty and the pursuit of happiness"
Dialogue: 0,1:21:02.40,1:21:04.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs14\b0\bord0\shad0}出自《独立宣言》
Dialogue: 0,1:21:04.99,1:21:07.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们曾为理想战斗  不该退让将就\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We fought for these ideals, we shouldn't settle for less
Dialogue: 0,1:21:07.84,1:21:10.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些智言慧语  有为之士常挂嘴边\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}These are wise words, enterprising men quote 'em
Dialogue: 0,1:21:10.73,1:21:13.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别故作惊讶  这些都出自我笔下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Don't act surprised, you guys, 'cause I wrote 'em
Dialogue: 0,1:21:14.69,1:21:15.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但汉密尔顿选择疏忽\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But Hamilton forgets
Dialogue: 0,1:21:15.98,1:21:18.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他计划让政府承担州债\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}His plan would have the government assume states' debts
Dialogue: 0,1:21:18.82,1:21:21.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们打个赌  最后谁受益\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now, place your bets as to who that benefits
Dialogue: 0,1:21:21.54,1:21:24.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是财政部长  汉密尔顿本人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The very seat of government where Hamilton sits
Dialogue: 0,1:21:24.23,1:21:26.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-不对  -既然是事实  就老实承认\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Not true! - Ooh, if the shoe fits, wear it
Dialogue: 0,1:21:26.92,1:21:30.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纽约欠债  凭什么让弗吉尼亚承担\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If New York's in debt, why should Virginia bear it?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:30.68,1:21:32.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们已无债一身轻\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Our debts are paid, I'm afraid
Dialogue: 0,1:21:32.22,1:21:35.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别看南方富足无虞  就给我们加税\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Don't tax the South 'cause we got it made in the shade
Dialogue: 0,1:21:35.49,1:21:38.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗吉尼亚人开垦土地  创造价值\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}In Virginia, we plant seeds in the ground, we create
Dialogue: 0,1:21:38.58,1:21:40.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你只是想挪用我们的资产\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You just wanna move our money around
Dialogue: 0,1:21:40.53,1:21:43.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这财政计划厚颜无耻\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This financial plan is an outrageous demand
Dialogue: 0,1:21:43.15,1:21:46.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还长篇大论  谁都看不懂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And it's too many damn pages for any man to understand
Dialogue: 0,1:21:46.62,1:21:48.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请和我守护这片自由土地\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Stand with me in the land of the free
Dialogue: 0,1:21:48.69,1:21:51.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向天祈祷  永远别让汉密尔顿参选\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Pray to God we never see Hamilton's candidacy
Dialogue: 0,1:21:51.21,1:21:53.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,英国向我们征茶税  我们奋起反抗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Look, when Britain taxed our tea, we got frisky
Dialogue: 0,1:21:54.28,1:21:57.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是你敢征酒税  想想后果会如何\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Imagine what gon' happen when you try to tax our whiskey
Dialogue: 0,1:21:57.70,1:21:59.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢  杰斐逊国务卿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Thank you, Secretary Jefferson.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:02.63,1:22:06.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汉密尔顿部长  请回应\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Secretary Hamilton, your response.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:08.06,1:22:10.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托马斯  算你舌灿莲花\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Thomas, that was a real nice declaration
Dialogue: 0,1:22:10.84,1:22:13.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回到现实  我们不是在过家家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Welcome to the present, we're running a real nation
Dialogue: 0,1:22:13.58,1:22:16.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要加入我们  还是归隐田园\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Would you like to join us, or stay mellow
Dialogue: 0,1:22:16.01,1:22:19.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回老家蒙蒂塞洛歌舞升平\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Doin' whatever the hell it is you do in Monticello?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:19.29,1:22:21.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我们承担债务  联邦将会获得\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If we assume the debts, the Union gets
Dialogue: 0,1:22:21.57,1:22:24.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,财政刺激  新的信贷额度\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A new line of credit, a financial diuretic
Dialogue: 0,1:22:24.30,1:22:25.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是揣着明白装糊涂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How do you not get it?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:25.33,1:22:28.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有大胆争先  联邦才会强大\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If we're aggressive and competitive, the Union gets a boost
Dialogue: 0,1:22:28.22,1:22:30.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你宁愿一瓢冷水泼下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You'd rather give it a sedative?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:30.09,1:22:31.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奴隶主大谈公民权利\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A civics lesson from a slaver
Dialogue: 0,1:22:31.91,1:22:35.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邻居  你无债一身轻  靠的是免费劳力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hey, neighbor, your debts are paid 'cause you don't pay for labor
Dialogue: 0,1:22:35.50,1:22:37.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"南方人开垦土地  创造价值"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"We plant seeds in the South, we create"
Dialogue: 0,1:22:37.62,1:22:41.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大话不要停  地里是谁耕作的身影\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yeah, keep ranting, we know who's really doing the planting
Dialogue: 0,1:22:41.48,1:22:43.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有一事  启蒙时代先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And another thing, Mr. Age of Enlightenment
Dialogue: 0,1:22:41.48,1:22:46.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs14\b0\bord0\shad0}启蒙时代是指十七至十八世纪\N欧洲地区发生的一场知识及文化运动
Dialogue: 0,1:22:43.47,1:22:46.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你都没参战  少跟我说教\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Don't lecture me about the war you didn't fight in it
Dialogue: 0,1:22:46.46,1:22:49.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以为我怕你吗  我们差点死在战壕里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You think I'm frightened of you, man? We almost died in a trench
Dialogue: 0,1:22:49.26,1:22:51.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你却跟法国佬打得火热\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}While you were off getting high with the French
Dialogue: 0,1:22:51.73,1:22:54.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托马斯·杰斐逊  总统问什么都犹豫不决\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Thomas Jefferson, always hesitant with the President
Dialogue: 0,1:22:54.42,1:22:57.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寡言少语  没一个计划能得他首肯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Reticent, there isn't a plan he hasn't jettisoned
Dialogue: 0,1:22:57.18,1:22:59.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麦迪逊  你个疯子  别忘吃药\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Madison, you mad as a hatter, son, take your medicine
Dialogue: 0,1:22:59.92,1:23:02.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们的状态比国家债务还要不堪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Damn, you're in worse shape than the national debt is in
Dialogue: 0,1:23:02.83,1:23:05.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两个百无一用的废物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sittin' there useless as two shits
Dialogue: 0,1:23:05.01,1:23:08.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,转个身  撅起屁股  让我擦擦鞋底\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hey, turn around, bend over, I'll show you where my shoe fits
Dialogue: 0,1:23:08.56,1:23:09.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打断一下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Excuse me.
