Dialogue: 0,1:28:25.81,1:28:28.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果国会不批准  我会丢掉工作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I lose my job if we don't get this plan through congress
Dialogue: 0,1:28:28.19,1:28:31.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可以去探望我们的父亲\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We can all go stay with our father
Dialogue: 0,1:28:31.05,1:28:33.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}那里有片湖泊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There's a lake I know
