Dialogue: 0,1:28:53.36,1:28:54.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1}此刻我们活着\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}At how lucky we are
Dialogue: 0,1:28:53.58,1:28:56.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}定会千古留名\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You will make your mark
Dialogue: 0,1:28:54.74,1:28:57.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1}是多么幸运\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}To be alive right now
Dialogue: 0,1:28:56.16,1:28:58.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}闭上眼睛畅想\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Close your eyes and dream
