Dialogue: 0,1:28:58.37,1:29:01.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等夜幕落下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}when the night gets dark
Dialogue: 0,1:29:01.39,1:29:03.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歇一歇\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Take a break
Dialogue: 0,1:29:03.37,1:29:05.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我必须要让国会批准我的提案\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I have to get my plan through Congress.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:05.53,1:29:08.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能停歇  直到国会批准我的提案\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I can't stop till I get this plan through Congress.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:24.69,1:29:27.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炎炎夏日  无比心浮气躁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There's nothing like summer in the city
Dialogue: 0,1:29:29.89,1:29:33.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重压之下  有人邂逅美女\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Someone under stress meets someone looking pretty
Dialogue: 0,1:29:36.47,1:29:39.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风雨欲来  不安空中弥漫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There's trouble in the air, you can smell it
Dialogue: 0,1:29:39.17,1:29:41.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚历山大  孤独寂寞\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And Alexander's by himself
Dialogue: 0,1:29:41.93,1:29:43.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他来讲\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll let him tell it
Dialogue: 0,1:29:44.25,1:29:47.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一周没合过眼  心力交瘁  彻夜难寐\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I hadn't slept in a week, I was weak, I was awake
Dialogue: 0,1:29:47.25,1:29:50.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,私生之子  孤苦之人  亟需喘一口气\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You've never seen a bastard orphan more in need of a break
Dialogue: 0,1:29:50.56,1:29:53.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渴望安洁莉卡  思念我的妻子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Longing for Angelica, missing my wife
Dialogue: 0,1:29:53.26,1:29:55.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这时玛丽亚·雷诺兹翩然而至\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's when Miss Maria Reynolds walked into my life
Dialogue: 0,1:29:55.99,1:29:57.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}She said:
Dialogue: 0,1:29:57.10,1:29:59.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你是正人君子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I know you are a man of honor
Dialogue: 0,1:29:59.87,1:30:02.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很抱歉我来上门打扰\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm so sorry to bother you at home
Dialogue: 0,1:30:02.49,1:30:05.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我走投无路\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But I don't know where to go
Dialogue: 0,1:30:05.21,1:30:07.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只身前来见你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And I came here all alone
Dialogue: 0,1:30:07.89,1:30:08.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}She said:
Dialogue: 0,1:30:08.88,1:30:11.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的丈夫辜负与我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My husband's doin' me wrong
Dialogue: 0,1:30:11.04,1:30:13.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拳脚相加  沾花惹草\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Beatin' me, cheatin' me
Dialogue: 0,1:30:13.40,1:30:14.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,种种虐待\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mistreatin' me
Dialogue: 0,1:30:14.85,1:30:17.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然之间  他消失无踪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Suddenly he's up and gone
Dialogue: 0,1:30:17.92,1:30:20.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有维生的手段\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't have the means to go on
Dialogue: 0,1:30:20.00,1:30:22.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是我借钱给她  送她回家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So I offered her a loan, I offered to walk her home
Dialogue: 0,1:30:22.85,1:30:23.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}She said:
Dialogue: 0,1:30:23.79,1:30:25.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您真是个好人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're too kind, sir
Dialogue: 0,1:30:25.69,1:30:27.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我掏出三十块私房钱给她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I gave her 30 bucks that I had socked away
Dialogue: 0,1:30:27.92,1:30:29.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她住在一个街区外  她说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}She lived a block away, She said:
Dialogue: 0,1:30:29.72,1:30:31.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我家到了  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This one's mine, sir
Dialogue: 0,1:30:31.69,1:30:33.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后我说  "我该回家了"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Then I said "Well, I should head back home"
Dialogue: 0,1:30:33.95,1:30:34.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她涨红了脸\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}She turned red
Dialogue: 0,1:30:34.87,1:30:37.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带我走到床边  宽衣解带  并说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}She led me to her bed, let her legs spread and said:
Dialogue: 0,1:30:37.78,1:30:39.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Stay?
