Dialogue: 0,1:40:01.20,1:40:03.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我发誓  你的自尊会害死所有人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I swear, your pride will be the death of us all
Dialogue: 0,1:40:01.20,1:40:05.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs14\b0\bord0\shad0}出自圣经《箴言》
Dialogue: 0,1:40:03.44,1:40:05.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心  傲慢必将导致灭亡\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Beware, it goeth before the fall
Dialogue: 0,1:40:05.55,1:40:07.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本次的议题是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The issue on the table:
Dialogue: 0,1:40:07.60,1:40:10.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法国即将与英国开战\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}France is on the verge of war with England.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:10.33,1:40:12.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是为法国盟友提供资金和援助\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now, do we commit money and aid to our French allies,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:12.92,1:40:14.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是坐壁上观\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}or do we stay out of it?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:14.80,1:40:16.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记住  我对此事的决议\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Remember, my decision on this matter
Dialogue: 0,1:40:16.84,1:40:19.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无须经过国会批准\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}is not subject to congressional approval.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:16.84,1:40:21.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs14\b0\bord0\shad0}事实上此话不准确
Dialogue: 0,1:40:19.25,1:40:21.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们只需要说服我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The only one you have to convince is me.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:21.75,1:40:24.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰斐逊国务卿  请您发言\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Secretary Jefferson, you have the floor, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:25.46,1:40:27.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们命悬一线  亟需帮助之时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}When we were on death's door, when we were needy
Dialogue: 0,1:40:27.81,1:40:30.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们许下承诺  我们签署条约\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We made a promise, we signed a treaty
Dialogue: 0,1:40:27.81,1:40:30.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs14\b0\bord0\shad0}1778年签署的《法美同盟条约》及《友好商业条约》
Dialogue: 0,1:40:30.27,1:40:32.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们需要钱  需要枪  需要一丝转机\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We needed money and guns and half a chance
Dialogue: 0,1:40:32.43,1:40:34.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁提供了资金\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Uh, who provided those funds?
