Dialogue: 0,1:40:35.15,1:40:37.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们没有要求割地为盟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}In return, they didn't ask for land
Dialogue: 0,1:40:37.42,1:40:39.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要求我们承诺  有朝一日\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}only a promise that we'd lend a hand
Dialogue: 0,1:40:39.53,1:40:42.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们反抗压迫者  我们要伸出援手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and stand with them if they fought against oppressors
