Dialogue: 0,1:40:43.05,1:40:44.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我们该挺身而出\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but now is the time to stand
Dialogue: 0,1:40:44.50,1:40:47.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我们的兄弟肩并肩  反抗暴政\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}stand with our brothers as they fight against tyranny
Dialogue: 0,1:40:47.08,1:40:49.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道亚历山大·汉密尔顿站在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I know that Alexander Hamilton is here
