Dialogue: 0,1:40:56.20,1:40:58.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,散发着暴发户气息  穿得好似假冒皇室\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Smells like new money, dresses like fake royalty
Dialogue: 0,1:40:58.90,1:41:01.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一心只想出人头地\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Desperate to rise above his station
Dialogue: 0,1:41:01.03,1:41:04.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的一切言行都违背建国理念\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Everything he does betrays the ideals of our nation
Dialogue: 0,1:41:05.23,1:41:08.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总统先生  要是你不知道  这下看个清楚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ay, and if you don't know, now you know, Mr. President
Dialogue: 0,1:41:08.63,1:41:10.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢  杰斐逊国务卿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Thank you, Secretary Jefferson.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:11.32,1:41:13.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汉密尔顿部长  请回应\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Secretary Hamilton, your response.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:13.63,1:41:14.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骂他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Get him, boy!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:14.44,1:41:16.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给他好看\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Let him know right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:16.94,1:41:19.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一定是脑子进水\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You must be outta your goddamn mind
Dialogue: 0,1:41:19.27,1:41:22.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然认为总统会让我们的国家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If you think the president is gonna bring the nation to the brink
Dialogue: 0,1:41:22.61,1:41:25.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去干涉他国战乱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Of meddling in the middle of a military mess
Dialogue: 0,1:41:25.14,1:41:27.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这盘棋局  法国已丢王弃后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A game of chess, where France is queen and king-less
Dialogue: 0,1:41:25.14,1:41:30.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs14\b0\bord0\shad0}1793年路易十六被斩首
Dialogue: 0,1:41:27.89,1:41:30.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们与国王签署条约  但他早已人头落地\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We signed a treaty with a king, whose head is now in a basket
Dialogue: 0,1:41:30.72,1:41:32.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要不要拎起人头  问他意见\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Would you like to take it out and ask it
Dialogue: 0,1:41:32.70,1:41:34.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路易国王的脑袋  我们应该遵守条约吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"Oh, should we honor our treaty, King Louis's head?"
Dialogue: 0,1:41:34.89,1:41:36.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们随便吧  我早死透了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"Ah, do whatever you want. I'm super dead"
Dialogue: 0,1:41:36.97,1:41:38.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,够了  够了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Enough, enough!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:38.50,1:41:40.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-汉密尔顿说得对  -总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Hamilton is right. - Mr. President--
Dialogue: 0,1:41:40.12,1:41:42.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们自顾不暇  不能再起战火\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're too fragile to start another fight
Dialogue: 0,1:41:42.33,1:41:44.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先生  难道我们不为自由而战\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sir, do we not fight for freedom?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:44.53,1:41:46.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然  等法国人选出领袖\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sure, when the French figure out who's gonna lead 'em
Dialogue: 0,1:41:46.92,1:41:48.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人民正在领导\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The people are leading
Dialogue: 0,1:41:48.30,1:41:50.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人民正在暴动  两者有所不同\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The people are rioting. There's a difference
Dialogue: 0,1:41:50.32,1:41:52.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说实话  这让人有点忧虑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Frankly, it's a little disquieting
Dialogue: 0,1:41:52.10,1:41:54.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的理念让你看不清现实\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You would let your ideals blind you to reality
Dialogue: 0,1:41:54.43,1:41:55.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-汉密尔顿  -长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Hamilton? - Sir
Dialogue: 0,1:41:54.43,1:41:57.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs14\b0\bord0\shad0}1793年  华盛顿颁布《中立宣言》\N"对交战双方采取友好和不偏不倚"\N成为早期美国的基本外交政策
Dialogue: 0,1:41:55.17,1:41:56.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,起草一份中立声明\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Draft a statement of neutrality
Dialogue: 0,1:41:56.83,1:41:57.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, sir
Dialogue: 0,1:41:57.67,1:41:59.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道你忘了拉法耶特\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Did you forget Lafayette?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:59.46,1:42:00.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:00.13,1:42:02.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道你没有一丝歉意\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Have you an ounce of regret?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:02.09,1:42:04.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你积累债务  你积聚权力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You accumulate debt. You accumulate power
Dialogue: 0,1:42:04.56,1:42:06.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但在他们需要之时  你却忘恩负义\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yet in their hour of need you forget
Dialogue: 0,1:42:06.76,1:42:09.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉法耶特是个聪明人  他会理解的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Lafayette's a smart man, he'll be fine
Dialogue: 0,1:42:09.10,1:42:11.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别忘了  我跟他的交情更深\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And before he was your friend, he was mine
Dialogue: 0,1:42:11.57,1:42:14.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果世上每场革命我们都要参与\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If we try to fight in every revolution in the world
Dialogue: 0,1:42:14.09,1:42:16.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么永无止境  何时才能停手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We never stop. Where do we draw the line?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:16.11,1:42:18.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-巧舌如簧  -我承认\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- So quick-witted. - Alas, I admit it
Dialogue: 0,1:42:18.22,1:42:20.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-肯定是个好律师  -我的被告都无罪释放\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- I bet you were quite a lawyer - My defendants got acquitted
Dialogue: 0,1:42:21.73,1:42:23.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-总得有人提醒你  -什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Well, someone ought to remind you - What?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:23.69,1:42:25.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有华盛顿撑腰  你什么都不是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're nothing without Washington behind you
Dialogue: 0,1:42:25.82,1:42:27.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-汉密尔顿  -老爸叫你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Hamilton. - Daddy's calling.
