Dialogue: 0,1:42:52.26,1:42:55.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凡事皆有反作用力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Every action has its equal opposite reaction
Dialogue: 0,1:42:55.82,1:42:59.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜汉密尔顿所赐  我们的内阁派系纷争\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Thanks to Hamilton, our cabinet's fractured into factions
Dialogue: 0,1:42:59.14,1:43:01.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只需一点应力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Try not to crack under the stress
Dialogue: 0,1:43:01.05,1:43:02.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就要碎成分数\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're breaking down like fractions
Dialogue: 0,1:43:02.86,1:43:06.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在报纸上互相诋毁  谁也不肯退让\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We smack each other in the press, and we don't print retractions
Dialogue: 0,1:43:06.41,1:43:09.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看不惯他突如其来的激情\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I get no satisfaction witnessing his fits of passion
Dialogue: 0,1:43:09.97,1:43:13.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,油头粉面  品味恶俗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The way he primps and preens and dresses like the pits of fashion
Dialogue: 0,1:43:13.53,1:43:17.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们穷苦的同胞  农民生活捉肘见襟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Our poorest citizens, our farmers live ration to ration
Dialogue: 0,1:43:17.14,1:43:21.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,华尔街大肆劫掠  不放过一毫一厘\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}as Wall Street robs 'em blind in search of chips to cash in
Dialogue: 0,1:43:21.08,1:43:23.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个混蛋就是欠教训\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This prick is asking for someone to bring him to task
Dialogue: 0,1:43:23.98,1:43:26.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁给我去挖这个蠢货的黑料\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Somebody give me some dirt on this vacuous mass
Dialogue: 0,1:43:26.13,1:43:27.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们能够揭露他的真面目\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So we can at last unmask him
Dialogue: 0,1:43:27.76,1:43:29.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我愿意扣下扳机\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll pull the trigger on him
