Dialogue: 0,1:44:09.78,1:44:11.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,审查他的政绩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Follow the scent of his enterprise
