Dialogue: 0,1:44:15.18,1:44:16.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不加制止  就是与之合谋\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If we don't stop it we aid and abet it
Dialogue: 0,1:44:16.94,1:44:17.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我必须辞职\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I have to resign
Dialogue: 0,1:44:17.89,1:44:19.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须有人挺身捍卫南方\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Somebody has to stand up for the South
Dialogue: 0,1:44:19.65,1:44:21.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须有人让他哑口无言\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Somebody has to stand up to his mouth
