Dialogue: 0,1:44:26.06,1:44:28.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼睁睁看他谗言惑君  春风得意\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I am complicit in watching him grabbin' at power and kiss it
Dialogue: 0,1:44:28.72,1:44:30.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然华盛顿心怀偏颇  不听异议\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If Washington isn't gon' listen to disciplined dissidents
Dialogue: 0,1:44:30.92,1:44:33.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这事不能忍  老子不干了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is the difference, this kid is out
Dialogue: 0,1:44:34.16,1:44:36.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个移民并非我们所选\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This immigrant isn't somebody we chose
Dialogue: 0,1:44:37.70,1:44:40.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个移民让我们惴惴不安\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This immigrant's keeping us all on our toes
Dialogue: 0,1:44:41.06,1:44:43.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让这些联邦党人好好长个教训\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Let's show these Federalists who they're up against
Dialogue: 0,1:44:44.65,1:44:47.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们牛逼的南方民主共和党人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Southern motherfukin' Democratic-Republicans
Dialogue: 0,1:44:48.44,1:44:51.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,追踪金钱的流向\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now follow the money and see where it goes
Dialogue: 0,1:44:52.23,1:44:54.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为财政部不断扩张\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Because every second the treasury grows
Dialogue: 0,1:44:55.85,1:44:58.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我们查出金钱的下落\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If we follow the money and see where it leads
Dialogue: 0,1:44:58.12,1:45:01.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掘地三尺  挖出汉密尔顿的罪行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Get in the weeds, look for the seeds of Hamilton's misdeeds
Dialogue: 0,1:45:01.66,1:45:03.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滋味一定不错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It must be nice
Dialogue: 0,1:45:03.78,1:45:05.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滋味一定不错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It must be nice
Dialogue: 0,1:45:06.58,1:45:08.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,追踪金钱的流向\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We follow the money and see where it goes
Dialogue: 0,1:45:08.91,1:45:10.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滋味一定不错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It must be nice
Dialogue: 0,1:45:10.97,1:45:13.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滋味一定不错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It must be nice
Dialogue: 0,1:45:14.17,1:45:16.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皇帝的新衣  我们来戳破\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The emperor has no clothes
Dialogue: 0,1:45:16.38,1:45:19.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不甘没落\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We won't be invisible
Dialogue: 0,1:45:19.97,1:45:21.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不容忽视\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We won't be denied
Dialogue: 0,1:45:22.18,1:45:24.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  滋味一定不错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Still, it must be nice
Dialogue: 0,1:45:24.98,1:45:27.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滋味一定不错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It must be nice
Dialogue: 0,1:45:27.64,1:45:31.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有华盛顿给你撑腰\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}To have Washington on your side
Dialogue: 0,1:45:32.35,1:45:34.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总统先生  您要见我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. President, you asked to see me.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:35.11,1:45:37.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你很忙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I know you're busy
Dialogue: 0,1:45:37.07,1:45:38.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您有什么需要\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What do you need, sir?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:39.70,1:45:40.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sir?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:40.36,1:45:43.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想给你提个醒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I wanna give you a word of warning
Dialogue: 0,1:45:43.12,1:45:44.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道您听了什么传言\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sir, I don't know what you heard,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:44.62,1:45:47.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但无论传言怎么说  都是杰斐逊挑起的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but whatever it is, Jefferson started it.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:48.70,1:45:52.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托马斯·杰斐逊今早辞职了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Thomas Jefferson resigned this morning
Dialogue: 0,1:45:52.21,1:45:53.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开玩笑吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're kidding.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:54.54,1:45:55.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要你帮个忙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I need a favor
Dialogue: 0,1:45:55.59,1:45:58.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任您吩咐  杰斐逊要付出代价\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Whatever you say, sir, Jefferson will pay for his behavior
Dialogue: 0,1:45:58.80,1:46:00.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少说话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Shh, talk less
Dialogue: 0,1:46:00.47,1:46:02.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以利用报纸  不会透露身份\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll use the press, I'll write under a pseudonym
Dialogue: 0,1:46:02.72,1:46:04.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等着瞧我批判他的劣行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You'll see what I can do to him
Dialogue: 0,1:46:04.72,1:46:06.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要你起草一份致辞\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I need you to draft an address
Dialogue: 0,1:46:06.72,1:46:09.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊  他辞职了  您终于不用顾忌了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, he resigned, you can finally speak your mind
Dialogue: 0,1:46:09.52,1:46:13.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  他辞职是为了竞选总统\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, he's stepping down so he can run for president
Dialogue: 0,1:46:13.77,1:46:15.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想打败您  祝他好运\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Good luck defeating you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:15.81,1:46:19.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要离职  不再参选\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm stepping down, I'm not running for president
Dialogue: 0,1:46:19.07,1:46:20.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您说什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm sorry, what?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:20.78,1:46:24.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后一次\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}One last time
Dialogue: 0,1:46:24.53,1:46:26.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我喝一杯  放轻松\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Relax, have a drink with me
Dialogue: 0,1:46:26.20,1:46:29.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后一次\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}One last time
Dialogue: 0,1:46:29.24,1:46:31.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚休息一下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Let's take a break tonight
Dialogue: 0,1:46:31.12,1:46:33.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后我们要教他们如何告别\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And then we'll teach 'em how to say goodbye
Dialogue: 0,1:46:33.96,1:46:35.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何告别\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}To say goodbye
Dialogue: 0,1:46:35.63,1:46:40.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You and I
Dialogue: 0,1:46:40.34,1:46:41.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  为什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, sir. Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:41.59,1:46:43.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想谈谈中立政策\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I want to talk about neutrality
Dialogue: 0,1:46:43.55,1:46:46.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长官  英法大战一触即发\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sir, with Britain and France on the verge of war
Dialogue: 0,1:46:46.64,1:46:47.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此时不宜...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Is this the best time--
Dialogue: 0,1:46:47.26,1:46:50.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想告诫党派斗争\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I want to warn against partisan fighting
Dialogue: 0,1:46:50.35,1:46:52.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿起笔  开始写\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Pick up a pen, start writing
Dialogue: 0,1:46:52.77,1:46:55.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想谈谈一生经验\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I wanna talk about what I have learned
Dialogue: 0,1:46:55.19,1:46:57.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教训中积累的智慧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The hard-won wisdom I have earned
Dialogue: 0,1:46:57.86,1:47:00.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在人民心中\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}As far as the people are concerned
Dialogue: 0,1:47:00.03,1:47:03.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您一定要连任  您完全可以连任\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You have to serve, you could continue to serve
Dialogue: 0,1:47:03.36,1:47:07.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  最后一次\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, one last time
Dialogue: 0,1:47:07.70,1:47:09.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他们听我谆谆忠告\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The people will hear from me
Dialogue: 0,1:47:09.24,1:47:12.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后一次\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}One last time
Dialogue: 0,1:47:12.62,1:47:14.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果做得好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And if we get this right
Dialogue: 0,1:47:14.29,1:47:18.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就能教他们如何告别\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're gonna teach 'em how to say goodbye
Dialogue: 0,1:47:18.46,1:47:25.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You and I
Dialogue: 0,1:47:25.09,1:47:27.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总统先生  他们会说您软弱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. President, they will say you're weak
Dialogue: 0,1:47:27.76,1:47:31.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  他们会明白我们的强大\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, they will see we're strong
Dialogue: 0,1:47:31.31,1:47:32.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您的地位独一无二\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Your position is so unique
Dialogue: 0,1:47:32.98,1:47:36.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就发挥作用  让权力交接\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So I'll use it to move them along
Dialogue: 0,1:47:36.19,1:47:38.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么您一定要离开\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Why do you have to say goodbye?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:38.23,1:47:40.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我离开了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If I say goodbye
Dialogue: 0,1:47:40.27,1:47:42.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,国家才能前进\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the nation learns to move on
Dialogue: 0,1:47:43.07,1:47:47.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不在了  它也永远繁荣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It outlives me when I'm gone
Dialogue: 0,1:47:49.41,1:47:51.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如同《圣经》所说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Like the scripture says
Dialogue: 0,1:47:51.74,1:47:57.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"人人都在自己的葡萄树和无花果树下安然居住\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"Everyone shall sit under their own vine and fig tree
Dialogue: 0,1:47:57.21,1:48:00.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无人惊吓他们"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And no one shall make them afraid"
Dialogue: 0,1:48:00.79,1:48:05.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们将在我们建立的国家安居乐业\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They'll be safe in the nation we've made
Dialogue: 0,1:48:06.26,1:48:11.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想坐在自己的葡萄树和无花果树下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I want to sit under my own vine and fig tree
Dialogue: 0,1:48:11.56,1:48:14.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在树荫下享片刻安宁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A moment alone in the shade
Dialogue: 0,1:48:15.23,1:48:20.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我们建立的国家中的家园\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}At home in this nation we've made
Dialogue: 0,1:48:21.19,1:48:24.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后一次\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}One last time
Dialogue: 0,1:48:24.78,1:48:27.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后一次\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}One last time?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:27.51,1:48:33.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs14\b0\bord0\shad0}1796年9月17日\N华盛顿发表著名的《告别辞》\N由汉密尔顿撰写\N此处节选结尾两段
Dialogue: 0,1:48:33.08,1:48:35.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然在检讨本人任期内施政时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Though, in reviewing the incidents of my administration,
Dialogue: 0,1:48:35.66,1:48:37.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有发现主观错误\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I am unconscious of intentional error,
Dialogue: 0,1:48:37.96,1:48:39.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我很清楚自身的缺点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I am nevertheless too sensible of my defects
Dialogue: 0,1:48:39.96,1:48:44.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深知我可能犯过很多错误\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}not to think it probable that I may have committed many errors.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:45.88,1:48:48.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也满怀希望\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I shall also carry with me the hope
Dialogue: 0,1:48:48.55,1:48:51.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愿我的国家宽恕这些错误\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that my country will view them with indulgence...
Dialogue: 0,1:48:51.68,1:48:57.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怀揣一颗赤诚之心  献身为国家服务\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And that after 45 years of my life dedicated to its service,
Dialogue: 0,1:48:57.02,1:48:59.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已有四十五年\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}with an upright zeal,
Dialogue: 0,1:48:59.14,1:49:00.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望我因为\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the faults of incompetent abilities
Dialogue: 0,1:49:00.65,1:49:03.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能力不足而犯的过失\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}will be consigned to oblivion,
Dialogue: 0,1:49:04.19,1:49:06.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会随着我不久以后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}as I myself must soon be
