Dialogue: 0,1:51:13.95,1:51:19.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乔治·华盛顿主动让权\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}George Washington's yielding his power and stepping away
Dialogue: 0,1:51:19.95,1:51:22.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:22.37,1:51:27.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都不知道还能这么做\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I wasn't aware that was something a person could do
Dialogue: 0,1:51:28.34,1:51:30.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好困惑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm perplexed
Dialogue: 0,1:51:30.75,1:51:35.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们要不断更换领袖吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Are they going to keep on replacing whoever's in charge?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:35.88,1:51:38.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那下一任是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If so, who's next?
