Dialogue: 0,1:51:58.45,1:52:00.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认识他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I know him
Dialogue: 0,1:52:00.45,1:52:02.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That can't be
