Dialogue: 0,1:52:05.75,1:52:07.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好多年前\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All those years ago
Dialogue: 0,1:52:07.87,1:52:10.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪年来着  1785\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What was it? '85
Dialogue: 0,1:52:10.29,1:52:14.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可怜的家伙  肯定要被生吞活剥\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That poor man, they're going to eat him alive
Dialogue: 0,1:52:14.13,1:52:18.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沧海桑田  王朝兴替\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oceans rise, empires fall
Dialogue: 0,1:52:18.05,1:52:21.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟华盛顿相比  他们都毫不起眼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Next to Washington they all look small
Dialogue: 0,1:52:21.89,1:52:23.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孤掌难鸣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All alone
Dialogue: 0,1:52:24.02,1:52:25.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看他们治国\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Watch them run
Dialogue: 0,1:52:25.85,1:52:29.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早晚斗个你死我活\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They will tear each other into pieces
Dialogue: 0,1:52:29.19,1:52:31.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天呐  等不及看戏了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Jesus Christ, this will be fun
