Dialogue: 0,1:52:47.37,1:52:48.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝你好运\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:56.30,1:52:58.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汉密尔顿  脾气暴躁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How does Hamilton, the short-tempered
Dialogue: 0,1:52:58.63,1:53:01.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反复无常  创建起了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}protean creator of the Coast Guard
Dialogue: 0,1:53:01.39,1:53:03.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海岸警卫队  和《纽约时报》\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Founder of the New York Post
Dialogue: 0,1:53:03.43,1:53:07.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然滥用职权  自毁声誉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}ardently abuse his cabinet post, destroy his reputation?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:07.89,1:53:11.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎来到亚当斯政府\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Welcome, folks, to the Adams administration!
Dialogue: 0,1:53:11.61,1:53:15.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰斐逊位列第二  担任副总统\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Jefferson's the runner-up, which makes him the vice president
Dialogue: 0,1:53:15.28,1:53:18.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,华盛顿帮不了你  再无好心总统\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Washington can't help you now, no more Mr. Nice President
Dialogue: 0,1:53:18.53,1:53:20.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚当斯开除汉密尔顿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Adams fires Hamilton
Dialogue: 0,1:53:20.24,1:53:23.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暗地里骂他  加勒比野种\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Privately calls him "creole bastard" in his taunts
Dialogue: 0,1:53:23.62,1:53:24.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Say what?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:24.16,1:53:27.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汉密尔顿公开反击\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hamilton publishes his response
Dialogue: 0,1:53:27.29,1:53:30.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我坐下  约翰  你个肥头大耳的混蛋\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sit down, John, you fat mother--
Dialogue: 0,1:53:32.75,1:53:33.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汉密尔顿狗急跳墙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hamilton's out of control.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:33.92,1:53:37.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了  他无权无势  没有公职\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is great. He's out of power, he holds no office,
Dialogue: 0,1:53:37.59,1:53:40.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还毁了约翰·亚当斯总统\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and he just destroyed President John Adams,
Dialogue: 0,1:53:40.22,1:53:42.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其政党仅剩的要员\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the only other significant member of his party.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:42.51,1:53:44.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汉密尔顿以一抵百\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hamilton is a host unto himself.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:44.26,1:53:47.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要手中有笔  就是威胁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}As long as he can hold a pen, he's a threat.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:47.14,1:53:49.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们去找他摊牌\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Let's let him know what we know.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:51.02,1:53:52.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,副总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Vice President
Dialogue: 0,1:53:54.19,1:53:55.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麦迪逊先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Madison
Dialogue: 0,1:53:56.61,1:53:58.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伯尔参议员\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Senator Burr
Dialogue: 0,1:53:59.15,1:54:00.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有何贵干\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What is this?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:00.78,1:54:03.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们手握多个账户的支票存根\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We have the check stubs from separate accounts
Dialogue: 0,1:54:03.53,1:54:06.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金额不一  合计近一千美元\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Almost a thousand dollars paid in different amounts
Dialogue: 0,1:54:06.28,1:54:09.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于1791年  支付给詹姆斯·雷诺兹先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}To a Mr. James Reynolds way back in 1791
Dialogue: 0,1:54:09.54,1:54:11.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是你们手中的把柄  说完了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Is that what you have? Are you done?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:11.50,1:54:14.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身为财政要员  你地位特殊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You are uniquely situated by virtue of your position
Dialogue: 0,1:54:14.50,1:54:17.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而此事跟"品德"毫不沾边\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Though "virtue" is not a word I'd apply to this situation
Dialogue: 0,1:54:17.30,1:54:20.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贪图金钱利益  背离神圣使命\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}To seek financial gain astray from your sacred mission
Dialogue: 0,1:54:20.22,1:54:23.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs14\b0\bord0\shad0}雷诺兹因投机倒把入狱\N谎称汉密尔顿也参与其中
Dialogue: 0,1:54:20.22,1:54:23.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有证据表明你投机倒把\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And the evidence suggests you've engaged in speculation
Dialogue: 0,1:54:23.22,1:54:25.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身为移民  侵吞政府资金\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}An immigrant embezzling our government funds
Dialogue: 0,1:54:25.72,1:54:28.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的倒台  已成定局\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I can almost see the headline your career is done
Dialogue: 0,1:54:28.52,1:54:31.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你给儿女留了口粮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I hope you saved some money for your daughter and sons
Dialogue: 0,1:54:31.39,1:54:34.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你最好从哪来的回哪去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You best g'wan run back where you come from
Dialogue: 0,1:54:35.65,1:54:38.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们甚至不知道想让我坦白什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You don't even know what you're asking me to confess
Dialogue: 0,1:54:38.98,1:54:40.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坦白\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Confess
Dialogue: 0,1:54:40.11,1:54:43.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们空口无凭  我不必多说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You have nothing I don't have to tell you anything at all
Dialogue: 0,1:54:43.82,1:54:45.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-除非  -除非\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Unless - Unless
Dialogue: 0,1:54:45.74,1:54:47.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我能自证从未犯法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If I can prove that I never broke the law
Dialogue: 0,1:54:47.95,1:54:51.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们能保证对此事守口如瓶吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Do you promise not to tell another soul what you saw?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:51.45,1:54:54.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,决策现场  再无他人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No one else was in the room where it happened
Dialogue: 0,1:54:54.17,1:54:55.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能保证吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Is that a yes?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:55.75,1:54:57.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Um, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:05.26,1:55:08.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"亲爱的先生  展信安\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"Dear sir, I hope this letter finds you in good health
Dialogue: 0,1:55:08.56,1:55:11.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愿您身居要职  家境富足\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And in a prosperous enough position to put wealth
Dialogue: 0,1:55:11.22,1:55:14.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有能力救济我这穷光蛋\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}In the pockets of people like me down on their luck
Dialogue: 0,1:55:14.06,1:55:16.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要知道  那可是我老婆被你..."\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You see, that was my wife who you decided to--"
Dialogue: 0,1:55:16.06,1:55:17.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:17.56,1:55:19.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她引诱我  骗我上床\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}She courted me, escorted me to bed
Dialogue: 0,1:55:19.57,1:55:21.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逼我走投无路\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And when she had me in a corner
Dialogue: 0,1:55:21.03,1:55:22.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被雷诺兹勒索\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's when Reynolds extorted me
Dialogue: 0,1:55:22.74,1:55:24.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,索要钱财  我按季支付\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}For a sordid fee, I paid him quarterly
Dialogue: 0,1:55:24.74,1:55:26.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算我的仕途无光\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I may have mortally wounded my prospects
Dialogue: 0,1:55:26.82,1:55:28.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我的账目明晰\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But my papers are orderly
Dialogue: 0,1:55:28.62,1:55:29.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如你们所见\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}As you can see,
Dialogue: 0,1:55:29.25,1:55:32.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的每笔开销都有记录\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I kept a record of every check in my checkered history
Dialogue: 0,1:55:32.08,1:55:35.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们自己核查  没有弄虚作假\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Check it again against your list and see consistency
Dialogue: 0,1:55:35.00,1:55:37.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我花的每一分都是自己的钱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I never spent a cent that wasn't mine
Dialogue: 0,1:55:37.13,1:55:39.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们派人调查  我不介意\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You sent the dogs after my scent, that's fine
Dialogue: 0,1:55:39.84,1:55:41.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对  我于心有愧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, I have reasons for shame
Dialogue: 0,1:55:41.92,1:55:45.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我没有犯叛国罪  没有糟蹋自己的名声\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But I have not committed treason and sullied my good name
Dialogue: 0,1:55:45.47,1:55:46.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如你们所见\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}As you can see,
Dialogue: 0,1:55:46.06,1:55:48.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没干违法乱纪的勾当\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I have done nothing to provoke legal action
Dialogue: 0,1:55:48.72,1:55:51.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个回答你们满意了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Are my answers to your satisfaction?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:53.14,1:55:54.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天呐\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My God.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:55.23,1:55:56.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先生们  我们走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Gentlemen, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:57.60,1:55:58.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:59.23,1:56:01.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会守口如瓶\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The people won't know what we know
Dialogue: 0,1:56:01.86,1:56:02.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伯尔\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Burr.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:02.86,1:56:05.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么知道下次针锋相对时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How do I know you won't use this against me
Dialogue: 0,1:56:05.32,1:56:07.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不会以此对付我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The next time we go toe to toe?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:07.86,1:56:11.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚历山大  谣言不胫而走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Alexander, rumors only grow
Dialogue: 0,1:56:11.37,1:56:15.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我们心照不宣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And we both know what we know
Dialogue: 0,1:56:31.93,1:56:35.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飓风之眼  反而宁静\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}In the eye of a hurricane, there is quiet
Dialogue: 0,1:56:37.14,1:56:39.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍纵即逝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}For just a moment
Dialogue: 0,1:56:41.36,1:56:42.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天空昏黄\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A yellow sky
Dialogue: 0,1:56:44.98,1:56:49.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十七岁时  飓风摧毁家乡\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}When I was 17, a hurricane destroyed my town
Dialogue: 0,1:56:49.66,1:56:52.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没淹死\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I didn't drown
Dialogue: 0,1:56:53.49,1:56:56.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仿佛不死之身\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I couldn't seem to die
Dialogue: 0,1:56:57.00,1:56:59.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我用笔墨开拓出路\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I wrote my way out
Dialogue: 0,1:57:00.33,1:57:04.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,写我目之所及\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Wrote everything down far as I could see
Dialogue: 0,1:57:05.84,1:57:08.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我用笔墨开拓出路\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I wrote my way out
Dialogue: 0,1:57:08.72,1:57:13.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我抬起头  乡亲注视着我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I looked up and the town had its eyes on me
Dialogue: 0,1:57:14.47,1:57:16.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们自发募捐\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They passed a plate around
Dialogue: 0,1:57:17.77,1:57:20.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,素不相识的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And total strangers
Dialogue: 0,1:57:20.60,1:57:23.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被我的故事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Moved to kindness
Dialogue: 0,1:57:23.44,1:57:25.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,激发出善意\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}By my story
Dialogue: 0,1:57:27.03,1:57:30.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,筹款为我购买船票\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Raised enough for me to book passage on a ship
Dialogue: 0,1:57:30.20,1:57:32.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前往纽约\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that was New York-bound
Dialogue: 0,1:57:33.49,1:57:36.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我用笔墨走出困境  我用笔墨推动革命\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I wrote my way out of hell, I wrote my way to revolution
Dialogue: 0,1:57:36.41,1:57:38.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我比自由钟还要响亮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I was louder than the crack in the bell
Dialogue: 0,1:57:38.33,1:57:41.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我给伊莱莎写信  赢得她的芳心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I wrote Eliza love letters until she fell
Dialogue: 0,1:57:41.21,1:57:44.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我声援宪法  誓死捍卫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I wrote about the Constitution and defended it well
Dialogue: 0,1:57:44.63,1:57:47.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,面对愚昧和抗拒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And in the face of ignorance and resistance
Dialogue: 0,1:57:47.21,1:57:50.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我创建金融体系\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I wrote financial systems into existence
Dialogue: 0,1:57:50.05,1:57:52.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我向上帝祈祷  却毫无回应\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And when my prayers to God were met with indifference
Dialogue: 0,1:57:52.60,1:57:56.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我拿起笔  自我救赎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I picked up a pen, I wrote my own deliverance
Dialogue: 0,1:57:56.10,1:58:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飓风之眼  反而宁静\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}In the eye of a hurricane, there is quiet
Dialogue: 0,1:58:01.23,1:58:03.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍纵即逝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}For just a moment
Dialogue: 0,1:58:05.57,1:58:06.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天空昏黄\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A yellow sky
Dialogue: 0,1:58:08.99,1:58:13.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十二岁时  母亲去世  她抱着我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I was 12 when my mother died, she was holding me
Dialogue: 0,1:58:13.45,1:58:16.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们病重  她抱着我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We were sick and she was holding me
Dialogue: 0,1:58:16.66,1:58:19.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仿佛不死之身\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I couldn't seem to die
Dialogue: 0,1:58:20.46,1:58:23.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn微软雅黑\fs15\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}等待  等待  等待\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Wait for it, wait for it, wait for it
