Dialogue: 0,1:58:24.26,1:58:26.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn微软雅黑\fs15\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}等待  等待  等待\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Wait for it, wait for it, wait for it
