Dialogue: 0,1:58:29.22,1:58:32.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn微软雅黑\fs15\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}等待  等待  等待  等待\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Wait for it, wait for it. Wait for it, wait for it
Dialogue: 0,1:58:30.93,1:58:37.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fn微软雅黑\fs15\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}你所做的一切  自有历史评判\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}History has its eyes on you
Dialogue: 0,1:58:32.26,1:58:35.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要用笔墨开拓出路\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll write my way out
Dialogue: 0,1:58:35.01,1:58:37.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用诚实压倒一切\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Overwhelm them with honesty
Dialogue: 0,1:58:37.51,1:58:39.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是飓风之眼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is the eye of the hurricane
