Dialogue: 0,1:58:50.44,1:58:51.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷诺兹手册\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The Reynolds pamphlet
Dialogue: 0,1:58:53.61,1:58:54.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Have you read this?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:54.91,1:58:58.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚历山大·汉密尔顿有一段风流韵事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Alexander Hamilton had a torrid affair
Dialogue: 0,1:58:58.74,1:59:00.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他全写出来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And he wrote it down right there
Dialogue: 0,1:59:00.79,1:59:01.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,精彩节选\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Highlights!
