Dialogue: 0,1:59:05.29,1:59:08.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行投机倒把之事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}For purposes of improper speculation
Dialogue: 0,1:59:08.17,1:59:11.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我真正的罪行是与他的妻子苟合\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My real crime is an amorous connection with his wife
Dialogue: 0,1:59:11.51,1:59:14.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关系长期维持  且他知情同意"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}For a considerable time with his knowing consent"
Dialogue: 0,1:59:14.68,1:59:15.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该死\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Damn
Dialogue: 0,1:59:15.76,1:59:19.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"我与她私会频繁  通常在我家里"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"I had frequent meetings with her, most of them at my own house"
Dialogue: 0,1:59:19.35,1:59:21.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-在他家里  -在他家里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- At his own house - At his own house
