Dialogue: 0,2:05:05.48,2:05:08.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姑娘们说我的魅力也不逊色\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The ladies say my brain's not where the resemblance stops
Dialogue: 0,2:05:08.49,2:05:10.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,年方十九  思想成熟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm only 19, but my mind is older
Dialogue: 0,2:05:10.82,2:05:13.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得自食其力  青出于蓝而胜于蓝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Gotta be my own man, like my father, but bolder
Dialogue: 0,2:05:13.87,2:05:15.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我骄傲地继承他的功绩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I shoulder his legacy with pride
Dialogue: 0,2:05:15.54,2:05:18.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾听他说过  有朝一日\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I used to hear him say that someday I would...
Dialogue: 0,2:05:18.25,2:05:19.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我将震撼环宇\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Blow us all away
Dialogue: 0,2:05:19.83,2:05:22.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女士们  我找乔治·伊克先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ladies, I'm looking for a Mr. George Eacker
Dialogue: 0,2:05:22.17,2:05:25.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上周国庆日演说的那位\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Made a speech last week, our Fourth of July speaker
Dialogue: 0,2:05:25.34,2:05:28.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在众人面前贬低我父亲的功绩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He disparaged my father's legacy In front of a crowd
Dialogue: 0,2:05:28.30,2:05:30.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我无法忍受  我要让父亲骄傲\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I can't have that, I'm making my father proud
Dialogue: 0,2:05:30.30,2:05:33.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看他去了百老汇那边\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I saw him just up Broadway a couple of blocks
Dialogue: 0,2:05:33.01,2:05:34.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他要去看戏\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He was going to see a play
Dialogue: 0,2:05:34.39,2:05:35.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我去包厢找他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, I'll go visit his box
Dialogue: 0,2:05:35.64,2:05:36.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊  你可真是迷人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}God, you're a fox
Dialogue: 0,2:05:36.77,2:05:38.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们的打扮也不赖\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Y'all look pretty good in your frocks
Dialogue: 0,2:05:38.43,2:05:41.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等我回来  咱们都把衣服脱光吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How 'bout when I get back we all strip down to our socks?
Dialogue: 0,2:05:41.77,2:05:43.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Okay!
Dialogue: 0,2:05:43.23,2:05:45.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,震撼环宇\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Blow us all away
Dialogue: 0,2:05:52.74,2:05:53.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乔治\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}George!
Dialogue: 0,2:05:53.82,2:05:55.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-乔治  -我在看戏呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- George. - I'm trying to watch the show.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:55.45,2:05:56.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你早该管好你的嘴\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You should've watched your mouth
Dialogue: 0,2:05:56.37,2:05:58.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少嚼我父亲的舌根\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Before you talked about my father though
Dialogue: 0,2:05:58.37,2:06:00.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可没说不实之事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I didn't say anything that wasn't true
Dialogue: 0,2:06:00.41,2:06:03.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你父亲是个无赖  看来你也一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Your father's a scoundrel and so, it seems, are you
Dialogue: 0,2:06:04.39,2:06:06.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你认真的  -对  我可没开玩笑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- It's like that? - Yeah, I don't fool around
Dialogue: 0,2:06:06.08,2:06:07.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不是学校里的小朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm not your little schoolboy friends
Dialogue: 0,2:06:07.54,2:06:09.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就决斗场上见\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, see you on the dueling ground
Dialogue: 0,2:06:09.27,2:06:11.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除非你想现在就出去比试一番\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That is, unless you wanna step outside and go now
Dialogue: 0,2:06:11.79,2:06:14.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道去哪找到你  滚吧  我在看戏呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I know where to find you, piss off, I'm watching the show now
Dialogue: 0,2:06:20.03,2:06:22.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老爸  你要是听到他的言论\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Pops, if you had only heard the shit he said about you
Dialogue: 0,2:06:22.35,2:06:24.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定不会置之不理  我也一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I doubt you would have let it slide and I was not about to
Dialogue: 0,2:06:24.91,2:06:26.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-慢着  -我来寻求你的建议\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Slow down. - I came to ask you for advice
Dialogue: 0,2:06:26.90,2:06:28.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我的第一场决斗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is my very first duel
Dialogue: 0,2:06:28.34,2:06:30.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寄宿学校没有这门课\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They don't exactly cover this subject in boarding school
Dialogue: 0,2:06:30.84,2:06:33.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的朋友尝试讲和了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Did your friends attempt to negotiate a peace?
Dialogue: 0,2:06:33.27,2:06:36.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他拒绝道歉  讲和是不可能了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He refused to apologize. We had to let the peace talks cease
Dialogue: 0,2:06:36.34,2:06:39.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-决斗地点在哪  -河对岸  新泽西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Where is this happening? - Across the river, in Jersey
Dialogue: 0,2:06:39.94,2:06:41.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在新泽西一切都是合法的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Everything is legal in New Jersey
Dialogue: 0,2:06:41.96,2:06:43.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All right
Dialogue: 0,2:06:43.18,2:06:44.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要照我说的做\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So, this is what you're gonna do
Dialogue: 0,2:06:44.58,2:06:47.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像个男人一样面对伊克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Stand there like a man until Eacker is in front of you
Dialogue: 0,2:06:47.31,2:06:50.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待时机到来  瞄准天空开枪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}When the time comes, fire your weapon in the air
Dialogue: 0,2:06:50.64,2:06:53.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圆满解决这件事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This will put an end to the whole affair
Dialogue: 0,2:06:53.61,2:06:55.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万一他决定对我开枪  我就死定了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But what if he decides to shoot? Then I'm a goner
Dialogue: 0,2:06:55.60,2:06:58.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  如果他是正人君子  他也会照做\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, he'll follow suit if he's truly a man of honor
Dialogue: 0,2:06:58.47,2:07:01.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夺取他人性命  罪孽深重无法摆脱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}To take someone's life, that is something you can't shake
Dialogue: 0,2:07:01.53,2:07:04.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利普  你母亲承受不了再次心碎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Philip, your mother can't take another heartbreak
Dialogue: 0,2:07:01.53,2:07:04.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs14\b0\bord0\shad0}除了显而易见的心碎之外\N安洁莉卡的妹妹佩吉·斯凯勒于1801年去世
Dialogue: 0,2:07:04.22,2:07:05.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-父亲  -答应我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Father-- - Promise me
Dialogue: 0,2:07:05.84,2:07:09.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别让你的良心沾上这位年轻人的鲜血\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You don't want this young man's blood on your conscience
Dialogue: 0,2:07:09.29,2:07:10.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  我答应\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Okay, I promise
Dialogue: 0,2:07:10.25,2:07:12.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结束之后就回家来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Come back home when you're done
Dialogue: 0,2:07:12.01,2:07:13.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿上我的枪  机灵点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Take my guns, be smart
Dialogue: 0,2:07:13.77,2:07:15.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要让我骄傲  孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Make me proud, son
Dialogue: 0,2:07:15.24,2:07:17.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫菲利普  我是个诗人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My name is Philip, I am a poet
Dialogue: 0,2:07:18.37,2:07:20.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有点紧张  但不能表露\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And I'm a little nervous but I can't show it
Dialogue: 0,2:07:21.04,2:07:23.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  我是汉密尔顿骄傲的后人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm sorry, I'm a Hamilton with pride
Dialogue: 0,2:07:23.13,2:07:26.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你诽谤我父亲  我不能置之不理\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You talk about my father, I cannot let it slide
Dialogue: 0,2:07:26.36,2:07:29.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊克先生  你的戏看得怎么样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Eacker, how was the rest of your show?
Dialogue: 0,2:07:29.03,2:07:31.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想寒暄  开始吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'd rather skip the pleasantries. Let's go
Dialogue: 0,2:07:31.71,2:07:34.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-拿好你的枪  -和同伴商量好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Grab your pistol. - Confer with your men
Dialogue: 0,2:07:34.15,2:07:36.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,数到十后决斗开始\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The duel will commence after we count to ten
Dialogue: 0,2:07:36.55,2:07:37.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,数到十\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Count to ten
Dialogue: 0,2:07:37.69,2:07:39.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盯着对方的眼睛  别瞄高了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Look 'em in the eye, aim no higher
Dialogue: 0,2:07:39.68,2:07:41.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鼓起全部勇气\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Summon all the courage you require
Dialogue: 0,2:07:41.70,2:07:44.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后缓慢坚定地  举枪瞄准天空\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Then slowly and clearly, aim your gun towards the sky
Dialogue: 0,2:07:44.88,2:07:47.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一  二  三  四  五  六  七\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}One, two, three, four, five, six, seven...
Dialogue: 0,2:07:53.76,2:07:59.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn微软雅黑\fs15\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}活下去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Stay alive
Dialogue: 0,2:07:59.68,2:08:05.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn微软雅黑\fs15\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}活下去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Stay alive
Dialogue: 0,2:08:00.88,2:08:01.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我儿子在哪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Where's my son?
Dialogue: 0,2:08:01.75,2:08:03.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汉密尔顿先生  请进\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Hamilton, come in.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:03.31,2:08:05.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是半小时前被送来的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They brought him in a half an hour ago.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:05.21,2:08:06.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在途中失血很多\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He lost a lot of blood on the way over.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:06.12,2:08:07.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-他还活着吗  -是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Is he alive? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:07.87,2:08:09.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你要明白\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But you have to understand,
Dialogue: 0,2:08:09.29,2:08:11.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,子弹从臀部上方射入  卡在他的右臂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the bullet entered just above his hip and lodged in his right arm.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:11.68,2:08:14.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我能看看他吗  -我在全力救治\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Can I see him, please? - I'm doing everything I can.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:14.97,2:08:17.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是他抵达时  伤口已经感染\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But the wound was already infected when he arrived.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:20.48,2:08:21.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利普\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Philip.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:23.13,2:08:23.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Pa.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:25.13,2:08:28.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我完全照你说的做了  爸\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I did exactly as you said, Pa
Dialogue: 0,2:08:29.02,2:08:31.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我昂首挺胸\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I held my head up high
Dialogue: 0,2:08:31.03,2:08:32.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白  我明白\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I know, I know, shh
Dialogue: 0,2:08:32.80,2:08:34.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-昂首挺胸  -我明白  我明白\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- High. - I know, I know, shh
Dialogue: 0,2:08:34.03,2:08:37.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白你做得很好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I know you did everything just right
Dialogue: 0,2:08:37.16,2:08:40.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没数到十\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Even before we got to ten
Dialogue: 0,2:08:40.99,2:08:42.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就瞄准了天空\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I was aiming for the sky
Dialogue: 0,2:08:42.93,2:08:44.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白  我明白\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I know, I know, shh
