Dialogue: 0,2:22:32.06,2:22:35.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神情严肃  仿佛身负使命\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Looking to the world like a man on a mission
Dialogue: 0,2:22:35.17,2:22:38.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是个弹无虚发的士兵\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is a soldier with a marksman's ability
Dialogue: 0,2:22:38.03,2:22:41.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,医生转身  方便事后推诿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The doctor turned around so he could have deniability
Dialogue: 0,2:22:41.19,2:22:42.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn微软雅黑\fs15\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}第五\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Five
Dialogue: 0,2:22:42.11,2:22:43.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当时我并不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now, I didn't know this at the time
Dialogue: 0,2:22:43.88,2:22:46.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们正站在你儿子丧命之处\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But we were near the same spot your son died
Dialogue: 0,2:22:46.33,2:22:47.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许这就为何\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Is that why
Dialogue: 0,2:22:47.37,2:22:48.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn微软雅黑\fs15\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}第六\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Six
Dialogue: 0,2:22:48.03,2:22:50.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他如此慎重地检查枪支\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He examined his gun with such rigor?
Dialogue: 0,2:22:50.38,2:22:53.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看着他有条不紊地摆弄扳机\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I watched as he methodically fiddled with the trigger
Dialogue: 0,2:22:53.35,2:22:54.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn微软雅黑\fs15\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}第七\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Seven
Dialogue: 0,2:22:54.13,2:22:56.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该坦白了  我得说实话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Confession time. Here's what I got
Dialogue: 0,2:22:56.27,2:22:59.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的战友都知道我枪法差劲\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My fellow soldiers'll tell you I'm a terrible shot
Dialogue: 0,2:22:56.27,2:22:59.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs14\b0\bord0\shad0}此话不实
Dialogue: 0,2:22:59.25,2:23:00.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn微软雅黑\fs15\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}第八\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Number eight
Dialogue: 0,2:23:00.29,2:23:02.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后的协商机会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Your last chance to negotiate
Dialogue: 0,2:23:02.69,2:23:03.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,派出副手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Send in your seconds
Dialogue: 0,2:23:03.85,2:23:06.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看是否能澄清误会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}See if they can set the record straight
Dialogue: 0,2:23:06.47,2:23:08.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,历史课上不会教这个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They won't teach you this in your classes
Dialogue: 0,2:23:08.70,2:23:11.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们去查查  汉密尔顿当时把眼镜戴起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But look it up, Hamilton was wearing his glasses
Dialogue: 0,2:23:11.97,2:23:15.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道不是为了将我毙命于抢下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Why, if not to take deadly aim?
Dialogue: 0,2:23:15.51,2:23:18.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一山不容二虎  世界从此不同\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's him or me. The world will never be the same
Dialogue: 0,2:23:18.72,2:23:21.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开枪之前我只有一个念头\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I had only one thought before the slaughter
Dialogue: 0,2:23:21.35,2:23:24.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此人休想让我女儿沦为孤儿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This man will not make an orphan of my daughter
Dialogue: 0,2:23:24.11,2:23:25.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fn微软雅黑\fs15\bord1\3c&H2F2F2F&\i1}第九\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Number nine
Dialogue: 0,2:23:25.43,2:23:27.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盯着对方的眼睛  别瞄高了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Look him in the eyes, aim no higher
Dialogue: 0,2:23:27.65,2:23:30.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鼓起全部勇气\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Summon all the courage you require
Dialogue: 0,2:23:30.01,2:23:30.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后数数\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Then count
Dialogue: 0,2:23:30.78,2:23:34.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一  二  三  四  五  六  七  八  九\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}One, two, three, four Five, six, seven, eight, nine
Dialogue: 0,2:23:34.19,2:23:35.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-几步  -十步\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Number! - Ten paces!
Dialogue: 0,2:23:35.42,2:23:36.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开枪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Fire!
Dialogue: 0,2:23:37.57,2:23:40.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我时常想象死亡  熟悉得如同回忆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I imagine death so much it feels more like a memory
Dialogue: 0,2:23:40.88,2:23:42.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是我的死期吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Is this where it gets me
Dialogue: 0,2:23:42.23,2:23:44.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站着等子弹袭来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}On my feet, several feet ahead of me?
Dialogue: 0,2:23:45.29,2:23:45.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看着它逼近\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I see it coming
Dialogue: 0,2:23:45.95,2:23:48.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是该逃跑  反击  还是认命\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Do I run or fire my gun or let it be?
Dialogue: 0,2:23:49.93,2:23:52.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有鼓点  没有旋律\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There is no beat, no melody
Dialogue: 0,2:23:52.65,2:23:55.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伯尔  我最初的朋友  我的宿敌\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Burr, my first friend, my enemy
Dialogue: 0,2:23:56.27,2:23:58.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许是我死前见到的最后一人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Maybe the last face I ever see
Dialogue: 0,2:23:58.65,2:24:01.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我放过良机射偏\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If I throw away my shot
Dialogue: 0,2:24:01.28,2:24:03.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世人对我的看法是否将如此被定义\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Is this how you remember me?
Dialogue: 0,2:24:05.55,2:24:07.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果这颗子弹就是我留下的功绩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What if this bullet is my legacy?
Dialogue: 0,2:24:07.60,2:24:08.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,功绩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Legacy
Dialogue: 0,2:24:09.16,2:24:11.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,何为功绩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What is a legacy?
Dialogue: 0,2:24:11.10,2:24:14.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,功绩是殷勤播种  却无缘见其绽放\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's planting seeds in a garden you never get to see
Dialogue: 0,2:24:14.55,2:24:16.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我谱下乐曲的序章\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I wrote some notes at the beginning of a song
Dialogue: 0,2:24:16.70,2:24:17.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将由后人来吟唱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}someone will sing for me
Dialogue: 0,2:24:17.79,2:24:20.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美利坚  你这曲未完成的宏伟交响\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}America, you great unfinished symphony
Dialogue: 0,2:24:20.14,2:24:22.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你召唤我  是你让我有所作为\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You sent for me. You let me make a difference
Dialogue: 0,2:24:22.99,2:24:24.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你让我这个移民孤儿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A place where even orphan immigrants
Dialogue: 0,2:24:24.63,2:24:26.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挥墨史书  出人头地\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Can leave their fingerprints and rise up
Dialogue: 0,2:24:26.66,2:24:29.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没时间了  没时间了  我的死期将至\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm running out of time, I'm running and my time's up
Dialogue: 0,2:24:29.02,2:24:31.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,动脑筋  抬起头\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Wise up, eyes up
Dialogue: 0,2:24:32.05,2:24:34.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我瞥见另一个世界\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I catch a glimpse of the other side
Dialogue: 0,2:24:34.59,2:24:37.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,劳伦斯在那边带领士兵们合唱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Laurens leads a soldiers' chorus on the other side
Dialogue: 0,2:24:37.46,2:24:39.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我儿子也在那边\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My son is on the other side
Dialogue: 0,2:24:39.38,2:24:41.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他和我母亲在一起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He's with my mother on the other side
Dialogue: 0,2:24:41.39,2:24:43.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,华盛顿在那边看着我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Washington is watching from the other side
Dialogue: 0,2:24:43.96,2:24:46.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教他们如何告别\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Teach me how to say goodbye
Dialogue: 0,2:24:46.31,2:24:49.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,崛起  崛起  崛起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Rise up. Rise up. Rise up.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:49.37,2:24:50.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊莱莎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Eliza!
Dialogue: 0,2:24:50.73,2:24:53.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亲爱的  尽情享受人生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My love, take your time.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:56.80,2:24:59.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们另一个世界再会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll see you on the other side.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:09.76,2:25:12.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,举杯敬自由\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Raise a glass to freedom
Dialogue: 0,2:25:12.87,2:25:14.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他举枪瞄准天空\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He aims his pistol at the sky.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:14.58,2:25:16.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Wait!
Dialogue: 0,2:25:19.91,2:25:22.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我击中他的肋间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I strike him right between his ribs
Dialogue: 0,2:25:25.28,2:25:28.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我朝他走去  却被催促离开\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I walk towards him, but I am ushered away
Dialogue: 0,2:25:32.04,2:25:34.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们带他渡回哈德逊河对岸\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They row him back across the Hudson
Dialogue: 0,2:25:37.99,2:25:39.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喝了一杯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I get a drink
Dialogue: 0,2:25:44.02,2:25:47.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听到街上传来哀号\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I hear wailing in the streets
Dialogue: 0,2:25:49.80,2:25:52.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人跟我说  "你最好躲起来"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Somebody tells me, "You'd better hide"
Dialogue: 0,2:25:55.85,2:25:59.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们说安洁莉卡和伊莱莎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They say Angelica and Eliza
Dialogue: 0,2:26:00.65,2:26:03.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在他临终时都伴在身侧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Were both at his side when he died
Dialogue: 0,2:26:04.18,2:26:08.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死亡不分罪人圣徒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Death doesn't discriminate between the sinners and the saints
Dialogue: 0,2:26:08.61,2:26:11.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它不断索取\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It takes and it takes and it takes
Dialogue: 0,2:26:11.04,2:26:15.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,历史冲刷掉一幕幕\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}History obliterates in every picture it paints
Dialogue: 0,2:26:15.17,2:26:18.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加深我的种种过错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It paints me in all my mistakes
Dialogue: 0,2:26:18.39,2:26:21.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚历山大举枪瞄准天空\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}When Alexander aimed at the sky
Dialogue: 0,2:26:21.84,2:26:24.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他虽先一步撒手人寰\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He may have been the first one to die
Dialogue: 0,2:26:24.56,2:26:27.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我却要苟活赎罪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But I'm the one who paid for it
Dialogue: 0,2:26:28.77,2:26:31.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,捡回一命  却罪责难逃\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I survived, but I paid for it
Dialogue: 0,2:26:34.86,2:26:38.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我成了你们史书中的罪人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now I'm the villain in your history
Dialogue: 0,2:26:40.78,2:26:46.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我太年轻盲目  执迷不悟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I was too young and blind to see
Dialogue: 0,2:26:46.74,2:26:50.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我早该知道  我早该知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I should've known, I should've known
Dialogue: 0,2:26:50.84,2:26:53.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界之大\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The world was wide enough
Dialogue: 0,2:26:53.30,2:26:58.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,容得下汉密尔顿和我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}For both Hamilton and me
Dialogue: 0,2:27:01.51,2:27:04.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界之大\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The world was wide enough
Dialogue: 0,2:27:04.93,2:27:11.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,容得下汉密尔顿和我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}For both Hamilton and me
Dialogue: 0,2:27:17.00,2:27:20.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,年轻时的我梦想荣耀\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Let me tell you what I wish I'd known
Dialogue: 0,2:27:20.16,2:27:23.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多希望那时我就懂得\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}When I was young and dreamed of glory
Dialogue: 0,2:27:23.73,2:27:25.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你无法左右\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You have no control
Dialogue: 0,2:27:25.39,2:27:29.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁生  谁死  谁讲述你的故事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Who lives? Who dies? Who tells your story?
Dialogue: 0,2:27:29.51,2:27:30.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰斐逊总统\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}President Jefferson.
